module: address-tracker-impl
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(address-tracker-impl)
      +--rw timestamp-update-interval?   uint32
      +--rw observe-addresses-from?      string
      +--rw notification-service
      |  +--rw type    service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw data-broker
         +--rw type?   service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
module: address-tracker
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/inv:node-connector:
   +--rw addresses* [id]
      +--rw id            uint64
      +--rw mac?          yang:mac-address
      +--rw ip?           inet:ip-address
      +--rw vlan?         ethernet:vlan-id
      +--rw first-seen?   int64
      +--rw last-seen?    int64
module: arp-handler-impl
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(arp-handler-impl)
      +--rw arp-flow-table-id?               uint8
      +--rw arp-flow-priority?               uint16
      +--rw arp-flow-hard-timeout?           uint16
      +--rw arp-flow-idle-timeout?           uint16
      +--rw flood-flow-table-id?             uint8
      +--rw flood-flow-priority?             uint16
      +--rw flood-flow-hard-timeout?         uint16
      +--rw flood-flow-idle-timeout?         uint16
      +--rw flood-flow-installation-delay?   uint32
      +--rw is-proactive-flood-mode?         boolean
      +--rw notification-service
      |  +--rw type    service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw data-broker
      |  +--rw type?   service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw rpc-registry
         +--rw type    service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
module: arp-packet
notifications:
   +---n arp-packet-received    
      +--ro packet-chain*
      |  +--ro (packet)?
      |     +--:(raw-packet)
      |        +--ro ingress?             inv:node-connector-ref
      |        +--ro connection-cookie?   pprocessing:connection-cookie
      |        +--ro flow-cookie?         flow-type:flow-cookie
      |        +--ro table-id?            table-type:table-id
      |        +--ro packet-in-reason?    identityref
      |        +--ro match
      |        |  +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |        |  +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |        |  +--ro metadata
      |        |  |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
      |        |  |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
      |        |  +--ro tunnel
      |        |  |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
      |        |  |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |        |  +--ro ethernet-match
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-source!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-type!
      |        |  |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
      |        |  +--ro vlan-match
      |        |  |  +--ro vlan-id!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |        |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |        |  |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |        |  +--ro ip-match
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |        |  +--ro (layer-3-match)?
      |        |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |        |  |  +--:(arp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
      |        |  |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |        |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  +--ro (layer-4-match)?
      |        |  |  +--:(udp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |        |  |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |        |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |        |  |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |        |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |        |  |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |        |  |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |        |  +--ro icmpv4-match
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |        |  +--ro icmpv6-match
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |        |  +--ro protocol-match-fields
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro pbb
      |        |  |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
      |        |  |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
      |        |  +--ro tcp-flag-match
      |        |     +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
      |        +--ro payload-offset?      int32
      |        +--ro payload-length?      int32
      +--ro payload?        binary
module: config
   +--rw modules
   |  +--rw module* [type name]
   |     +--rw name    string
   |     +--rw type    identityref
   |     +--rw (configuration)
   |     +--ro (state)?
   +--rw services
      +--rw service* [type]
         +--rw type        service-type-ref
         +--rw instance* [name]
            +--rw name        string
            +--rw provider    -> /modules/module/name
module: ethernet-packet
notifications:
   +---n ethernet-packet-received    
      +--ro packet-chain*
      |  +--ro (packet)?
      |     +--:(raw-packet)
      |        +--ro ingress?             inv:node-connector-ref
      |        +--ro connection-cookie?   pprocessing:connection-cookie
      |        +--ro flow-cookie?         flow-type:flow-cookie
      |        +--ro table-id?            table-type:table-id
      |        +--ro packet-in-reason?    identityref
      |        +--ro match
      |        |  +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |        |  +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |        |  +--ro metadata
      |        |  |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
      |        |  |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
      |        |  +--ro tunnel
      |        |  |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
      |        |  |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |        |  +--ro ethernet-match
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-source!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-type!
      |        |  |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
      |        |  +--ro vlan-match
      |        |  |  +--ro vlan-id!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |        |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |        |  |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |        |  +--ro ip-match
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |        |  +--ro (layer-3-match)?
      |        |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |        |  |  +--:(arp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
      |        |  |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |        |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  +--ro (layer-4-match)?
      |        |  |  +--:(udp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |        |  |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

      |        |  |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |        |  |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

      |        |  |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |        |  |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number

      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |        |  +--ro icmpv6-match
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8

      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32

      |        |  |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32

      |        |     +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
      |        +--ro payload-offset?      int32
      |        +--ro payload-length?      int32
      +--ro payload?        binary
module: flow-capable-transaction
rpcs:
   +---x get-next-transaction-id    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?   inv:node-ref
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x finish-transaction         
      +---w input     
         +---w node?             inv:node-ref
         +---w transaction-id?   transaction-id
module: flow-node-inventory
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node:
   +--rw manufacturer?             string
   +--rw hardware?                 string
   +--rw software?                 string
   +--rw serial-number?            string
   +--rw description?              string
   +--rw table* [id]
   |  +--rw id                  uint8
   |  +--rw table-features* [table-id]
   |  |  +--rw table-id            uint8
   |  |  +--rw name?               string
   |  |  +--rw metadata-match?     uint64
   |  |  +--rw metadata-write?     uint64
   |  |  +--rw max-entries?        uint32
   |  |  +--rw config?             table-config
   |  |  +--rw table-properties
   |  |     +--rw table-feature-properties* [order]
   |  |        +--rw order                  int32
   |  |        +--rw (table-feature-prop-type)?
   |  |           +--:(instructions)
   |  |           |  +--rw instructions
   |  |           |     +--rw instruction* [order]
   |  |           |        +--rw order             int32
   |  |           |        +--rw (instruction)?
   |  |           |           +--:(go-to-table-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw go-to-table
   |  |           |           |     +--rw table_id?   uint8
   |  |           |           +--:(write-metadata-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw write-metadata
   |  |           |           |     +--rw metadata?        uint64
   |  |           |           |     +--rw metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |           +--:(write-actions-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw write-actions
   |  |           |           |     +--rw action* [order]
   |  |           |           |        +--rw order                  int32
   |  |           |           |        +--rw (action)?
   |  |           |           |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +--rw output-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw max-length?              uint16
   |  |           |           |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +--rw controller-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw max-length?   uint16
   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +--rw set-field
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw metadata
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw metadata?        uint64
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw tunnel
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw ethernet-match
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-source!
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-destination!
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-type!
   |  |           |           |           |     |     +--rw type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw vlan-match
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw vlan-id!
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw ip-match
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw (layer-3-match)?
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-label
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  |  +--rw flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-ext-header
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |     +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |     +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |           |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw (layer-4-match)?
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |           |           |           |     |     +--rw sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |           |     |     +--rw sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw icmpv4-match
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw icmpv6-match
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw protocol-match-fields
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--rw pbb
   |  |           |           |           |     |     +--rw pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |           |           |           |     |     +--rw pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw tcp-flag-match
   |  |           |           |           |        +--rw tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +--rw set-queue-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw queue?      string
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw queue-id?   uint32
   |  |           |           |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +--rw pop-mpls-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +--rw set-mpls-ttl-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +--rw set-nw-ttl-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +--rw nw-ttl?   uint8

   |  |           |           |     +--rw vlan-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw vlan-id!
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           |           |     +--rw ip-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |           |           |     +--rw (layer-3-match)?
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix

   |  |           |           |  +--rw set-tp-src-action
   |  |           |           |     +--rw port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |           |           |     +--rw vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw set-vlan-id-action
   |  |           |           |     +--rw vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |           |           |     +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw strip-vlan-action
   |  |           |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |           |              +--rw sw-path-action
   |  |           +--:(apply-actions-miss)
   |  |           |  +--rw apply-actions-miss
   |  |           |     +--rw action* [order]
   |  |           |        +--rw order                  int32
   |  |           |        +--rw (action)?
   |  |           |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw output-action
   |  |           |           |     +--rw output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |           |           |     +--rw max-length?              uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw controller-action
   |  |           |           |     +--rw max-length?   uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw set-field
   |  |           |           |     +--rw in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |           |     +--rw in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |           |     +--rw metadata
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw metadata?        uint64
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw metadata-mask?   uint64

   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |           |     +--rw ethernet-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-source!
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-destination!
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-type!
   |  |           |           |     |     +--rw type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |           |           |     +--rw vlan-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw vlan-id!
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           |           |     +--rw ip-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |           |           |     +--rw (layer-3-match)?
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-label
   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +--rw flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-ext-header

   |  |           |           |     |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-hardware-address!

   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     +--rw (layer-4-match)?
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +--rw tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |     +--rw sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |     +--rw sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     +--rw icmpv4-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw icmpv4-code?   uint8

   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     +--rw protocol-match-fields

   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +--rw mpls-bos?     uint8

   |  |           |           |     |     +--rw pbb-mask?   uint32

   |  |           |           |        +--rw tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)

   |  |           |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)

   |  |           |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw set-tp-src-action

   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)

   |  |           |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +--rw strip-vlan-action
   |  |           |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |           |              +--rw sw-path-action
   |  |           +--:(match)
   |  |           |  +--rw match-setfield
   |  |           |     +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(wildcards)
   |  |           |  +--rw wildcard-setfield
   |  |           |     +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(write-setfield)
   |  |           |  +--rw write-setfield
   |  |           |     +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(write-setfield-miss)
   |  |           |  +--rw write-setfield-miss
   |  |           |     +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(apply-setfield)
   |  |           |  +--rw apply-setfield
   |  |           |     +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(apply-setfield-miss)
   |  |              +--rw apply-setfield-miss
   |  |                 +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |                    +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |                    +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  +--rw flow* [id]
   |  |  +--rw id                flow-id
   |  |  +--rw match
   |  |  |  +--rw in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |  +--rw in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |  |  |  |  +--rw metadata-mask?   uint64

   |  |  |  |  +--rw tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |  +--rw ethernet-match
   |  |  |  |  +--rw ethernet-source!

   |  |  |  |  +--rw ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |  |  +--rw ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |  |  +--rw ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |  +--rw (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)

   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address

   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address

   |  |  |  +--rw (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw tunnel

   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-type!
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +--rw type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw vlan-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw vlan-id!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw ip-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-label

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--rw flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-hardware-address!

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address

   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)

   |  |  |        |           |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw (layer-4-match)?

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |  |  |        |           |  +--rw set-dl-src-action

   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw group-id?   uint32

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)

   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |              |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |     +--rw (layer-4-match)?
   |              |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |              |     |  |  +--rw udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |              |     |  |  +--rw udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |              |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |              |     |  |  +--rw tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |              |     |  |  +--rw tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |              |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |              |     |     +--rw sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |              |     |     +--rw sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |              |     +--rw icmpv4-match
   |              |     |  +--rw icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |              |     |  +--rw icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |              |     +--rw icmpv6-match
   |              |     |  +--rw icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |              |     |  +--rw icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |              |     +--rw protocol-match-fields
   |              |     |  +--rw mpls-label?   uint32
   |              |     |  +--rw mpls-tc?      uint8
   |              |     |  +--rw mpls-bos?     uint8
   |              |     |  +--rw pbb
   |              |     |     +--rw pbb-isid?   uint32
   |              |     |     +--rw pbb-mask?   uint32
   |              |     +--rw tcp-flag-match
   |              |        +--rw tcp-flag?   uint16
   |              +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-queue-action
   |              |     +--rw queue?      string
   |              |     +--rw queue-id?   uint32
   |              +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw pop-mpls-action
   |              |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
   |              +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-mpls-ttl-action

   |              +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-nw-ttl-action
   |              |     +--rw nw-ttl?   uint8
   |              +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

   |              |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
   |              +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw pop-pbb-action
   |              +--:(push-mpls-action-case)

   |              |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
   |              +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |              |  +--rw dec-mpls-ttl
   |              +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |              |  +--rw dec-nw-ttl

   |              |  +--rw drop-action
   |              +--:(flood-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw flood-action
   |              +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw flood-all-action
   |              +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw hw-path-action
   |              +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw loopback-action
   |              +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw pop-vlan-action
   |              +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw push-vlan-action
   |              |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
   |              |     +--rw tag?             int32
   |              |     +--rw pcp?             int32
   |              |     +--rw cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |              |     +--rw vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |              +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |              |  +--rw copy-ttl-out
   |              +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |              |  +--rw copy-ttl-in
   |              +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-dl-dst-action
   |              |     +--rw address?   yang:mac-address
   |              +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-dl-src-action
   |              |     +--rw address?   yang:mac-address
   |              +--:(group-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw group-action
   |              |     +--rw group?      string
   |              |     +--rw group-id?   uint32
   |              +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-dl-type-action
   |              |     +--rw dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |              +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-next-hop-action
   |              |     +--rw (address)?
   |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |              |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |              |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |              +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)

   |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |              |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |              |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |              +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-nw-src-action

   |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |              |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |              |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |              +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-nw-tos-action
   |              |     +--rw tos?   int32
   |              +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-tp-dst-action
   |              |     +--rw port?   inet:port-number
   |              +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-tp-src-action
   |              |     +--rw port?   inet:port-number
   |              +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-vlan-cfi-action
   |              |     +--rw vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |              +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-vlan-id-action
   |              |     +--rw vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |              +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-vlan-pcp-action
   |              |     +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |              +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw strip-vlan-action
   |              +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |                 +--rw sw-path-action
   +--rw meter* [meter-id]
   |  +--rw flags?                meter-flags
   |  +--rw meter-id              meter-id
   |  +--rw barrier?              boolean
   |  +--rw meter-name?           string
   |  +--rw container-name?       string
   |  +--rw meter-band-headers
   |     +--rw meter-band-header* [band-id]
   |        +--rw band-id                    band-id
   |        +--rw meter-band-types
   |        |  +--rw flags?   meter-band-type
   |        +--rw band-rate?                 uint32
   |        +--rw band-burst-size?           uint32
   |        +--rw (band-type)?
   |           +--:(drop)
   |           |  +--rw drop-rate?                 uint32
   |           |  +--rw drop-burst-size?           uint32
   |           +--:(dscp-remark)
   |           |  +--rw dscp-remark-rate?          uint32
   |           |  +--rw dscp-remark-burst-size?    uint32
   |           |  +--rw perc_level?                uint8
   |           +--:(experimenter)
   |              +--rw experimenter-rate?         uint32
   |              +--rw experimenter-burst-size?   uint32
   |              +--rw experimenter?              uint32
   +--rw ip-address?               inet:ip-address
   +--rw supported-match-types
   |  +--rw match-type* [match]
   |     +--rw support-state?   inv:support-type
   |     +--rw match            string
   +--rw supported-instructions
   |  +--rw instruction-type* [instruction]
   |     +--rw support-state?   inv:support-type
   |     +--rw instruction      string
   +--rw supported-actions
   |  +--rw action-type* [action]
   |     +--rw support-state?   inv:support-type
   |     +--rw action           string
   +--rw switch-features
      +--rw max_buffers?    uint32
      +--rw max_tables?     uint8
      +--rw capabilities*   identityref
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/inv:node-connector:
   +--rw port-number?           union
   +--rw hardware-address?      yang:mac-address
   +--rw configuration?         port-config
   +--rw advertised-features?   port-features
   +--rw name?                  string
   +--rw state
   |  +--rw link-down?   boolean
   |  +--rw blocked?     boolean
   |  +--rw live?        boolean
   +--rw current-feature?       port-features
   +--rw supported?             port-features
   +--rw peer-features?         port-features
   +--rw current-speed?         uint32
   +--rw maximum-speed?         uint32
   +--rw queue* [queue-id]
      +--rw queue-id    queue-id
      +--rw port?       uint32
      +--rw property?   uint16
augment /inv:node-updated:
   +---- manufacturer?             string
   +---- hardware?                 string
   +---- software?                 string
   +---- serial-number?            string
   +---- description?              string
   +---- table* [id]
   |  +---- id                uint8
   |  +---- table-features* [table-id]
   |  |  +---- table-id            uint8
   |  |  +---- name?               string

   |  |  +---- metadata-write?     uint64

   |  |           |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-id-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-pcp-action

   |  |           |           |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)

   |  |           |           |              +---- sw-path-action
   |  |           |           +--:(apply-actions-case)

   |  |           |           |     +---- action* [order]
   |  |           |           |        +---- order                  int32
   |  |           |           |        +---- (action)?
   |  |           |           |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- output-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- max-length?              uint16
   |  |           |           |           +--:(controller-action-case)

   |  |           |           |           |     +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |  |           |           |           |     |  +---- metadata-mask?   uint64

   |  |           |           |           |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- ethernet-match
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +---- ethernet-source!
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address

   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-ext-header
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-hardware-address!

   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           |           |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- strip-vlan-action
   |  |           |           |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |           |           |              +---- sw-path-action
   |  |           |           +--:(meter-case)
   |  |           |              +---- meter
   |  |           |                 +---- meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |  |           +--:(next-table)
   |  |           |  +---- tables
   |  |           |     +---- table-ids*   uint8
   |  |           +--:(next-table-miss)
   |  |           |  +---- tables-miss
   |  |           |     +---- table-ids*   uint8
   |  |           +--:(write-actions)
   |  |           |  +---- write-actions
   |  |           |     +---- action* [order]
   |  |           |        +---- order                  int32
   |  |           |        +---- (action)?
   |  |           |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- output-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |           |           |     +---- max-length?              uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- controller-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- max-length?   uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-field
   |  |           |           |     +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |           |     +---- in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |           |     +---- metadata
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- metadata?        uint64
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |           |     +---- tunnel
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |           |     +---- ethernet-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ethernet-source!
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address

   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ip-ecn?        uint8

   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix

   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-hardware-address!

   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address

   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number

   |  |           |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-dl-type-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |           |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-next-hop-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- (address)?
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-nw-dst-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- (address)?
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-nw-src-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- (address)?
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-nw-tos-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- tos?   int32
   |  |           |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-tp-dst-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-tp-src-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)

   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)

   |  |           |           |     +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- strip-vlan-action
   |  |           |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |           |              +---- sw-path-action
   |  |           +--:(apply-actions)
   |  |           |  +---- apply-actions
   |  |           |     +---- action* [order]
   |  |           |        +---- order                  int32
   |  |           |        +---- (action)?
   |  |           |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- output-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |           |           |     +---- max-length?              uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- controller-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- max-length?   uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-field
   |  |           |           |     +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |           |     +---- in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |           |     +---- metadata
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- metadata?        uint64
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |           |     +---- tunnel
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |           |     +---- ethernet-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ethernet-source!
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ethernet-destination!
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ethernet-type!
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |           |           |     +---- vlan-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- vlan-id!
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           |           |     +---- ip-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |           |           |     +---- (layer-3-match)?
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-label
   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +---- flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-ext-header
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     +---- (layer-4-match)?
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     +---- icmpv4-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     +---- icmpv6-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     +---- protocol-match-fields
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- pbb
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |           |           |     +---- tcp-flag-match
   |  |           |           |        +---- tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-queue-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- queue?      string

   |  |           |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)

   |  |           |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- pop-vlan-action

   |  |           |           |     +---- tag?             int32
   |  |           |           |     +---- pcp?             int32
   |  |           |           |     +---- cfi?             vlan-cfi

   |  |           |           |     +---- metadata

   |  |           |           |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64

   |  |           |           |     |  +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp

   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ip-proto?      inet:ip-version

   |  |           |           |  +---- dec-mpls-ttl
   |  |           |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- dec-nw-ttl
   |  |           |           +--:(drop-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- drop-action
   |  |           |           +--:(flood-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- flood-action
   |  |           |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- flood-all-action
   |  |           |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- hw-path-action
   |  |           |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- loopback-action
   |  |           |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- pop-vlan-action
   |  |           |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- push-vlan-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           |           |     +---- tag?             int32
   |  |           |           |     +---- pcp?             int32
   |  |           |           |     +---- cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |           |           |     +---- vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- copy-ttl-out
   |  |           |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- copy-ttl-in
   |  |           |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-dl-dst-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-dl-src-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           +--:(group-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- group-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- group?      string
   |  |           |           |     +---- group-id?   uint32
   |  |           |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-dl-type-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |           |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-next-hop-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- (address)?
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-nw-dst-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- (address)?
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-nw-src-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- (address)?
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-nw-tos-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- tos?   int32
   |  |           |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-tp-dst-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-tp-src-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-id-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)

   |  |           |           |     +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- strip-vlan-action
   |  |           |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |           |              +---- sw-path-action
   |  |           +--:(match)
   |  |           |  +---- match-setfield
   |  |           |     +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(wildcards)
   |  |           |  +---- wildcard-setfield
   |  |           |     +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(write-setfield)
   |  |           |  +---- write-setfield
   |  |           |     +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(write-setfield-miss)
   |  |           |  +---- write-setfield-miss
   |  |           |     +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(apply-setfield)
   |  |           |  +---- apply-setfield
   |  |           |     +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(apply-setfield-miss)
   |  |              +---- apply-setfield-miss
   |  |                 +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |                    +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |                    +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  +---- flow* [id]
   |     +---- id                flow-id
   |     +---- match
   |     |  +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  +---- in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  +---- metadata
   |     |  |  +---- metadata?        uint64
   |     |  |  +---- metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |  +---- tunnel
   |     |  |  +---- tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |  |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |  +---- ethernet-match
   |     |  |  +---- ethernet-source!
   |     |  |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  +---- ethernet-destination!
   |     |  |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  +---- ethernet-type!
   |     |  |     +---- type    l2t:ether-type
   |     |  +---- vlan-match
   |     |  |  +---- vlan-id!
   |     |  |  |  +---- vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |     |  |  |  +---- vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |  +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  +---- ip-match
   |     |  |  +---- ip-protocol?   uint8
   |     |  |  +---- ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |  |  +---- ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |  |  +---- ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |  +---- (layer-3-match)?
   |     |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-label
   |     |  |  |  |  +---- ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |  |  |  +---- flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-ext-header
   |     |  |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |     |  |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |  |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |  |  |  +---- arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |  |  |  +---- arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +---- arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +---- arp-source-hardware-address!
   |     |  |  |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- arp-target-hardware-address!
   |     |  |  |     +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |     +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |     |  |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  +---- (layer-4-match)?
   |     |  |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |  |  |  +---- udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  +---- udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |     |  |  |  +---- tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  +---- tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |     |  |     +---- sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |  |     +---- sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |     |  +---- icmpv4-match
   |     |  |  +---- icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |     |  |  +---- icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |     |  +---- icmpv6-match
   |     |  |  +---- icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |     |  |  +---- icmpv6-code?   uint8

   |     |  |  +---- mpls-tc?      uint8
   |     |  |  +---- mpls-bos?     uint8

   |     |  |     +---- pbb-isid?   uint32
   |     |  |     +---- pbb-mask?   uint32
   |     |  +---- tcp-flag-match
   |     |     +---- tcp-flag?   uint16
   |     +---- instructions
   |     |  +---- instruction* [order]
   |     |     +---- order             int32
   |     |     +---- (instruction)?
   |     |        +--:(go-to-table-case)

   |     |        |     +---- table_id?   uint8

   |     |        |     +---- metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |        +--:(write-actions-case)

   |     |        |        +---- order                  int32
   |     |        |        +---- (action)?
   |     |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- output-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |     |        |           |     +---- max-length?              uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)

   |     |        |           |     +---- max-length?   uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-field
   |     |        |           |     +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id

   |     |        |           |     +---- metadata

   |     |        |           |     |  +---- metadata-mask?   uint64

   |     |        |           |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64
