   |     |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-tp-src-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- port?   inet:port-number
   |     |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-vlan-cfi-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |     |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-vlan-id-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |     |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-vlan-pcp-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- strip-vlan-action
   |     |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |     |        |              +---- sw-path-action
   |     |        +--:(apply-actions-case)
   |     |        |  +---- apply-actions
   |     |        |     +---- action* [order]
   |     |        |        +---- order                  int32
   |     |        |        +---- (action)?
   |     |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- output-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |     |        |           |     +---- max-length?              uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- controller-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- max-length?   uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-field
   |     |        |           |     +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |        |           |     +---- in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     |        |           |     +---- metadata
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- metadata?        uint64
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |        |           |     +---- tunnel
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |        |           |     +---- ethernet-match
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ethernet-source!
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ethernet-destination!
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ethernet-type!
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- type    l2t:ether-type
   |     |        |           |     +---- vlan-match
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- vlan-id!
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |        |           |     +---- ip-match
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ip-protocol?   uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |        |           |     +---- (layer-3-match)?
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-label
   |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---- flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-ext-header
   |     |        |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |     |        |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-hardware-address!
   |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-hardware-address!
   |     |        |           |     |  |     +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |     +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     +---- (layer-4-match)?
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     +---- icmpv4-match
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |     |        |           |     +---- icmpv6-match
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |     |        |           |     +---- protocol-match-fields
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- mpls-label?   uint32
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- mpls-tc?      uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- mpls-bos?     uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- pbb
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- pbb-isid?   uint32
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- pbb-mask?   uint32
   |     |        |           |     +---- tcp-flag-match
   |     |        |           |        +---- tcp-flag?   uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-queue-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- queue?      string
   |     |        |           |     +---- queue-id?   uint32
   |     |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)

   |     |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)

   |     |        |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)

   |     |        |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)

   |     |        |           |     +---- tag?             int32
   |     |        |           |     +---- pcp?             int32
   |     |        |           |     +---- cfi?             vlan-cfi

   |     |        |           |     +---- (address)?

   |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)

   |     |        |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-dl-type-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |     |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-next-hop-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- (address)?
   |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |     |        |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |        |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)

   |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |     |        |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |        |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)

   |     |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-tp-src-action

   |     |              +---- meter-id?   meter:meter-id

   |     +---- idle-timeout?     uint16
   |     +---- hard-timeout?     uint16
   |     +---- cookie?           flow-cookie

   |     +---- cookie_mask?      flow-cookie

   |     +---- out_group?        uint32

   |     +---- barrier?          boolean
   |     +---- strict?           boolean

   |  +---- container-name?   string
   |  +---- barrier?          boolean

   |              |  +---- output-action
   |              |     +---- output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |              |     +---- max-length?              uint16

   |              |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |              |     +---- ethernet-match
   |              |     |  +---- ethernet-source!

   |              |     |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |              |     |  +---- ethernet-destination!

   |              |     |  +---- ip-ecn?        uint8

module: ietf-netconf-monitoring
   +--ro netconf-state
      +--ro capabilities
      |  +--ro capability*   inet:uri
      +--ro datastores
      |  +--ro datastore* [name]
      |     +--ro name     netconf-datastore-type
      |     +--ro locks!
      |        +--ro (lock-type)?
      |           +--:(global-lock)
      |           |  +--ro global-lock
      |           |     +--ro locked-by-session    uint32
      |           |     +--ro locked-time          yang:date-and-time
      |           +--:(partial-lock)
      |              +--ro partial-lock* [lock-id]
      |                 +--ro lock-id              uint32
      |                 +--ro locked-by-session    uint32
      |                 +--ro locked-time          yang:date-and-time
      |                 +--ro select*              yang:xpath1.0
      |                 +--ro locked-node*         instance-identifier
      +--ro schemas
      |  +--ro schema* [identifier version format]
      |     +--ro identifier    string
      |     +--ro version       string
      |     +--ro format        identityref
      |     +--ro namespace     inet:uri
      |     +--ro location*     union
      +--ro sessions
      |  +--ro session* [session-id]
      |     +--ro session-id           uint32
      |     +--ro transport            identityref
      |     +--ro username             string
      |     +--ro source-host?         inet:host
      |     +--ro login-time           yang:date-and-time
      |     +--ro in-rpcs?             yang:zero-based-counter32
      |     +--ro in-bad-rpcs?         yang:zero-based-counter32
      |     +--ro out-rpc-errors?      yang:zero-based-counter32
      |     +--ro out-notifications?   yang:zero-based-counter32
      +--ro statistics
         +--ro netconf-start-time?   yang:date-and-time
         +--ro in-bad-hellos?        yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro in-sessions?          yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro dropped-sessions?     yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro in-rpcs?              yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro in-bad-rpcs?          yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro out-rpc-errors?       yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro out-notifications?    yang:zero-based-counter32

      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |        |  |  +--:(arp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
      |        |  |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |        |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  +--ro (layer-4-match)?
      |        |  |  +--:(udp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |        |  |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |        |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |        |  |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |        |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |        |  |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |        |  |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |        |  +--ro icmpv4-match
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |        |  +--ro icmpv6-match
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |        |  +--ro protocol-match-fields
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro pbb
      |        |  |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
      |        |  |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
      |        |  +--ro tcp-flag-match
      |        |     +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
      |        +--ro payload-offset?      int32
      |        +--ro payload-length?      int32
      +--ro payload?        binary

            |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
            |     |  +--rw ethernet-destination!
            |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
            |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
            |     |  +--rw ethernet-type!
            |     |     +--rw type    l2t:ether-type
            |     +--rw vlan-match
            |     |  +--rw vlan-id!
            |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id-present?   boolean
            |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
            |     |  +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
            |     +--rw ip-match
            |     |  +--rw ip-protocol?   uint8
            |     |  +--rw ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
            |     |  +--rw ip-ecn?        uint8
            |     |  +--rw ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
            |     +--rw (layer-3-match)?
            |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
            |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
            |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
            |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
            |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
            |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
            |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
            |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-label
            |     |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
            |     |  |  |  +--rw flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
            |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
            |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
            |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-ext-header
            |     |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
            |     |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
            |     |  +--:(arp-match)
            |     |  |  +--rw arp-op?                         uint16
            |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
            |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
            |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-hardware-address!
            |     |  |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
            |     |  |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
            |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-hardware-address!
            |     |  |     +--rw address    yang:mac-address
            |     |  |     +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
            |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
            |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
            |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
            |     +--rw (layer-4-match)?
            |     |  +--:(udp-match)
            |     |  |  +--rw udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
            |     |  |  +--rw udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
            |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
            |     |  |  +--rw tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
            |     |  |  +--rw tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
            |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
            |     |     +--rw sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
            |     |     +--rw sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
            |     +--rw icmpv4-match
            |     |  +--rw icmpv4-type?   uint8
            |     |  +--rw icmpv4-code?   uint8
            |     +--rw icmpv6-match
            |     |  +--rw icmpv6-type?   uint8
            |     |  +--rw icmpv6-code?   uint8
            |     +--rw protocol-match-fields
            |     |  +--rw mpls-label?   uint32
            |     |  +--rw mpls-tc?      uint8
            |     |  +--rw mpls-bos?     uint8
            |     |  +--rw pbb
            |     |     +--rw pbb-isid?   uint32
            |     |     +--rw pbb-mask?   uint32
            |     +--rw tcp-flag-match
            |        +--rw tcp-flag?   uint16
            +--:(set-queue-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-queue-action
            |     +--rw queue?      string
            |     +--rw queue-id?   uint32
            +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
            |  +--rw pop-mpls-action
            |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
            +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-mpls-ttl-action
            |     +--rw mpls-ttl?   uint8
            +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-nw-ttl-action
            |     +--rw nw-ttl?   uint8
            +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
            |  +--rw push-pbb-action
            |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
            +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
            |  +--rw pop-pbb-action
            +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
            |  +--rw push-mpls-action
            |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
            +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
            |  +--rw dec-mpls-ttl
            +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
            |  +--rw dec-nw-ttl
            +--:(drop-action-case)
            |  +--rw drop-action
            +--:(flood-action-case)
            |  +--rw flood-action
            +--:(flood-all-action-case)
            |  +--rw flood-all-action
            +--:(hw-path-action-case)
            |  +--rw hw-path-action
            +--:(loopback-action-case)
            |  +--rw loopback-action
            +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
            |  +--rw pop-vlan-action
            +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
            |  +--rw push-vlan-action
            |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
            |     +--rw tag?             int32
            |     +--rw pcp?             int32
            |     +--rw cfi?             vlan-cfi
            |     +--rw vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
            +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
            |  +--rw copy-ttl-out
            +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
            |  +--rw copy-ttl-in
            +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-dl-dst-action
            |     +--rw address?   yang:mac-address
            +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-dl-src-action
            |     +--rw address?   yang:mac-address
            +--:(group-action-case)
            |  +--rw group-action
            |     +--rw group?      string
            |     +--rw group-id?   uint32
            +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-dl-type-action
            |     +--rw dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
            +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-next-hop-action
            |     +--rw (address)?
            |        +--:(ipv4)
            |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
            |        +--:(ipv6)
            |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
            +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-nw-dst-action
            |     +--rw (address)?
            |        +--:(ipv4)
            |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
            |        +--:(ipv6)
            |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
            +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-nw-src-action
            |     +--rw (address)?
            |        +--:(ipv4)
            |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
            |        +--:(ipv6)
            |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
            +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-nw-tos-action
            |     +--rw tos?   int32
            +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-tp-dst-action
            |     +--rw port?   inet:port-number
            +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-tp-src-action
            |     +--rw port?   inet:port-number
            +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-vlan-cfi-action
            |     +--rw vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
            +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-vlan-id-action
            |     +--rw vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
            +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-vlan-pcp-action
            |     +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
            +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
            |  +--rw strip-vlan-action
            +--:(sw-path-action-case)
               +--rw sw-path-action
module: opendaylight-flow-statistics
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/flow-node:table/flow-node:flow:
   +--rw flow-statistics
      +--rw packet-count?   yang:counter64
      +--rw byte-count?     yang:counter64
      +--rw duration
         +--rw second?       yang:counter32
         +--rw nanosecond?   yang:counter32
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/flow-node:table:
   +--rw aggregate-flow-statistics
      +--rw packet-count?   yang:counter64
      +--rw byte-count?     yang:counter64
      +--rw flow-count?     yang:counter32
rpcs:
   +---x get-all-flows-statistics-from-all-flow-tables                    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?   node-ref
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro flow-and-statistics-map-list* [flow-id]
   |     |  +--ro flow-id           flow-id
   |     |  +--ro match
   |     |  |  +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  |  +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  |  +--ro metadata
   |     |  |  |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |     |  |  |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |  +--ro tunnel
   |     |  |  |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |  |  |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |  +--ro ethernet-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-type!
   |     |  |  |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
   |     |  |  +--ro vlan-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id!
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |  |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  |  +--ro ip-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |  |  +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |     |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |     |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |  |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |     |  |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |     |  |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |  |  |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |     |  |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |     |  |  |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |     |  |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |     |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |     |  |  |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |     |  |  +--ro icmpv4-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |     |  |  +--ro icmpv6-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |     |  |  +--ro protocol-match-fields
   |     |  |  |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
   |     |  |  |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro pbb
   |     |  |  |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
   |     |  |  |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
   |     |  |  +--ro tcp-flag-match
   |     |  |     +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   |     |  +--ro instructions
   |     |  |  +--ro instruction* [order]
   |     |  |     +--ro order             int32
   |     |  |     +--ro (instruction)?
   |     |  |        +--:(go-to-table-case)
   |     |  |        |  +--ro go-to-table
   |     |  |        |     +--ro table_id?   uint8
   |     |  |        +--:(write-metadata-case)

   |     |  |        |     +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |        +--:(write-actions-case)

   |     |  |        |     +--ro action* [order]
   |     |  |        |        +--ro order                  int32
   |     |  |        |        +--ro (action)?
   |     |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro output-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?              uint16

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-field
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro metadata
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro tunnel
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ip-match

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16

   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-ttl-action

   |     |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro push-mpls-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro dec-mpls-ttl

   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp

   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro icmpv4-match
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro icmpv6-match
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro pbb
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
   |     |  |        |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-queue-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro queue?      string
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action

   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro nw-ttl?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro push-mpls-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)

   |     |  |        |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro dec-nw-ttl
   |     |  |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           +--:(flood-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro hw-path-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(loopback-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro pop-vlan-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro tag?             int32

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)

   |     |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)

   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |     |  |        |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |     |  |        +--:(meter-case)
   |     |  |           +--ro meter
   |     |  |              +--ro meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |     |  +--ro priority?         uint16
   |     |  +--ro idle-timeout?     uint16
   |     |  +--ro hard-timeout?     uint16
   |     |  +--ro cookie?           flow-cookie
   |     |  +--ro table_id?         uint8
   |     |  +--ro container-name?   string
   |     |  +--ro cookie_mask?      flow-cookie
   |     |  +--ro buffer_id?        uint32
   |     |  +--ro out_port?         uint64
   |     |  +--ro out_group?        uint32
   |     |  +--ro flags?            flow-mod-flags
   |     |  +--ro flow-name?        string
   |     |  +--ro installHw?        boolean
   |     |  +--ro barrier?          boolean
   |     |  +--ro strict?           boolean
   |     |  +--ro packet-count?     yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro byte-count?       yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro duration
   |     |     +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |     |     +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |     +--ro transaction-id?                 transaction-id

   |  |  +---w table-id?   table-types:table-id

   |     |  +--ro match
   |     |  |  +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  |  +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |     |  |  |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |     |  |  |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64

   |     |  |  |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |  |  |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |  +--ro ethernet-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-source!

   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-destination!

   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

   |     |  |  +--ro vlan-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id!
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |  |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  |  +--ro ip-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |  |  +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |     |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix

   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro icmpv4-match

   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |     |  |        |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |     |  |        +--:(clear-actions-case)
   |     |  |        |  +--ro clear-actions
   |     |  |        |     +--ro action* [order]
   |     |  |        |        +--ro order                  int32
   |     |  |        |        +--ro (action)?
   |     |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro output-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro controller-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-field
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro metadata
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro tunnel
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-match
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ip-match
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro icmpv4-match
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro icmpv6-match
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro pbb
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
   |     |  |        |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-queue-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro queue?      string
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-ttl-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro nw-ttl?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro push-pbb-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro pop-pbb-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro push-mpls-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro dec-mpls-ttl
   |     |  |        |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro dec-nw-ttl
   |     |  |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro drop-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(flood-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro flood-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro flood-all-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro hw-path-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro loopback-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro pop-vlan-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro push-vlan-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro tag?             int32
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro pcp?             int32
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-out
   |     |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-in
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-dl-dst-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-dl-src-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           +--:(group-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro group-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro group?      string
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro group-id?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-dl-type-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-next-hop-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |     |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-dst-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |     |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-src-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |     |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |     |  |        |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |     |  |        +--:(meter-case)
   |     |  |           +--ro meter
   |     |  |              +--ro meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |     |  +--ro priority?         uint16
   |     |  +--ro idle-timeout?     uint16
   |     |  +--ro hard-timeout?     uint16
   |     |  +--ro cookie?           flow-cookie
   |     |  +--ro table_id?         uint8
   |     |  +--ro container-name?   string
   |     |  +--ro cookie_mask?      flow-cookie
   |     |  +--ro buffer_id?        uint32
   |     |  +--ro out_port?         uint64
   |     |  +--ro out_group?        uint32
   |     |  +--ro flags?            flow-mod-flags
   |     |  +--ro flow-name?        string
   |     |  +--ro installHw?        boolean
   |     |  +--ro barrier?          boolean
   |     |  +--ro strict?           boolean
   |     |  +--ro packet-count?     yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro byte-count?       yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro duration
   |     |     +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |     |     +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |     +--ro transaction-id?                 transaction-id
   +---x get-flow-statistics-from-flow-table                              
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?             node-ref
   |  |  +---w match
   |  |  |  +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |  +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |  +---w metadata
   |  |  |  |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |  |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |  +---w tunnel
   |  |  |  |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |  |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |  +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |  |  |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |  +---w vlan-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |  +---w ip-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |  +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-label
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |  |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |  |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |  +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |  |  +---w icmpv6-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |  +---w protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |  |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |  |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w pbb
   |  |  |  |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |  |  |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |  +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |     +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  +---w instructions
   |  |  |  +---w instruction* [order]
   |  |  |     +---w order             int32
   |  |  |     +---w (instruction)?
   |  |  |        +--:(go-to-table-case)
   |  |  |        |  +---w go-to-table
   |  |  |        |     +---w table_id?   uint8
   |  |  |        +--:(write-metadata-case)
   |  |  |        |  +---w write-metadata
   |  |  |        |     +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |     +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        +--:(write-actions-case)
   |  |  |        |  +---w write-actions
   |  |  |        |     +---w action* [order]
   |  |  |        |        +---w order                  int32
   |  |  |        |        +---w (action)?
   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w output-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w controller-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-field
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w metadata
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tunnel
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ip-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w pbb
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-queue-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tag?             int32

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-out
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-in
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(group-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w group-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w group?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w group-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-type-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-next-hop-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(clear-actions-case)
   |  |  |        |  +---w clear-actions
   |  |  |        |     +---w action* [order]
   |  |  |        |        +---w order                  int32
   |  |  |        |        +---w (action)?
   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w output-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
