   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w metadata
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tunnel
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ip-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w pbb
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-queue-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tag?             int32

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(group-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(meter-case)
   |  |  |           +---w meter
   |  |  |              +---w meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |  |  +---w priority?         uint16
   |  |  +---w idle-timeout?     uint16
   |  |  +---w hard-timeout?     uint16
   |  |  +---w cookie?           flow-cookie
   |  |  +---w table_id?         uint8
   |  |  +---w container-name?   string
   |  |  +---w cookie_mask?      flow-cookie
   |  |  +---w buffer_id?        uint32
   |  |  +---w out_port?         uint64
   |  |  +---w out_group?        uint32
   |  |  +---w flags?            flow-mod-flags
   |  |  +---w flow-name?        string
   |  |  +---w installHw?        boolean
   |  |  +---w barrier?          boolean
   |  |  +---w strict?           boolean
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro flow-and-statistics-map-list* [flow-id]
   |     |  +--ro flow-id           flow-id
   |     |  +--ro match
   |     |  |  +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  |  +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  |  +--ro metadata
   |     |  |  |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |     |  |  |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |  +--ro tunnel
   |     |  |  |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |  |  |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |  +--ro ethernet-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-type!
   |     |  |  |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
   |     |  |  +--ro vlan-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id!
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |  |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  |  +--ro ip-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |  |  +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |     |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |     |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |  |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |     |  |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |     |  |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |  |  |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |     |  |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |     |  |  |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |     |  |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |     |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |     |  |  |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |     |  |  +--ro icmpv4-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |     |  |  +--ro icmpv6-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |     |  |  +--ro protocol-match-fields
   |     |  |  |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
   |     |  |  |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro pbb
   |     |  |  |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
   |     |  |  |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
   |     |  |  +--ro tcp-flag-match
   |     |  |     +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   |     |  +--ro instructions
   |     |  |  +--ro instruction* [order]
   |     |  |     +--ro order             int32
   |     |  |     +--ro (instruction)?
   |     |  |        +--:(go-to-table-case)
   |     |  |        |  +--ro go-to-table

   |     |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id

   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!

   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-match
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!

   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id

   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix

   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro pbb
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
   |     |  |        |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-queue-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro queue?      string
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
   |     |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

   |     |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

   |     |  |              +--ro meter-id?   meter:meter-id

   |     |  +--ro out_group?        uint32

   |     |  +--ro installHw?        boolean

   |     |  +--ro byte-count?       yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro duration

   |     +--ro transaction-id?                 transaction-id

   |  |  +---w table-id?   table-types:table-id

   +---x get-aggregate-flow-statistics-from-flow-table-for-given-match    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w node?             node-ref
      |  +---w match
      |  |  +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  |  +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |  |  +---w metadata
      |  |  |  +---w metadata?        uint64
      |  |  |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  |  +---w tunnel
      |  |  |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
      |  |  |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |  +---w ethernet-match
      |  |  |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  +---w ethernet-destination!
      |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  +---w ethernet-type!
      |  |  |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
      |  |  +---w vlan-match
      |  |  |  +---w vlan-id!
      |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |  |  |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |  +---w ip-match
      |  |  |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
      |  |  |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |  |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |  |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |  +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-label
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
      |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |  |  |  +--:(arp-match)
      |  |  |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
      |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |  |  |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |  |  |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |  |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |  |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |  |  |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |  |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |  |  |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |  |  |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |  |  +---w icmpv4-match
      |  |  |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |  |  |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |  |  +---w icmpv6-match
      |  |  |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |  |  |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |  |  +---w protocol-match-fields

      |  |  |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
      |  |  |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8

      |  |  |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
      |  |  |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  |  +---w tcp-flag-match
      |  |     +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
      |  +---w instructions
      |  |  +---w instruction* [order]
      |  |     +---w order             int32
      |  |     +---w (instruction)?
      |  |        +--:(go-to-table-case)
      |  |        |  +---w go-to-table
      |  |        |     +---w table_id?   uint8
      |  |        +--:(write-metadata-case)

      |  |        |     +---w metadata?        uint64
      |  |        |     +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  |        +--:(write-actions-case)

      |  |        |     +---w action* [order]
      |  |        |        +---w order                  int32
      |  |        |        +---w (action)?
      |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
      |  |        |           |  +---w output-action
      |  |        |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
      |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
      |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)

      |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
      |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
      |  |        |           |  +---w set-field
      |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |  |        |           |     +---w metadata

      |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)

      |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

      |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number

   |  +--ro moreReplies?                    boolean

   |  |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-type!
   |  |  |  |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |  +--ro vlan-match
   |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id!
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |  +--ro ip-match
   |  |  |  |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |  |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |  |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |  +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |  |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |  |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |  |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |  +--ro icmpv4-match
   |  |  |  |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |  |  +--ro icmpv6-match
   |  |  |  |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |  +--ro protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |  |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |  |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |  |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8

   |  |  |  |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |  |  |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |  +--ro tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |     +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  +--ro instructions
   |  |  |  +--ro instruction* [order]
   |  |  |     +--ro order             int32
   |  |  |     +--ro (instruction)?
   |  |  |        +--:(go-to-table-case)
   |  |  |        |  +--ro go-to-table
   |  |  |        |     +--ro table_id?   uint8
   |  |  |        +--:(write-metadata-case)
   |  |  |        |  +--ro write-metadata
   |  |  |        |     +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |     +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        +--:(write-actions-case)

   |  |  |        |     +--ro action* [order]
   |  |  |        |        +--ro order                  int32
   |  |  |        |        +--ro (action)?
   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro output-action

   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?              uint16

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?

   |  |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(meter-case)
   |  |  |           +--ro meter
   |  |  |              +--ro meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |  |  +--ro priority?         uint16
   |  |  +--ro idle-timeout?     uint16
   |  |  +--ro hard-timeout?     uint16
   |  |  +--ro cookie?           flow-cookie
   |  |  +--ro table_id?         uint8
   |  |  +--ro container-name?   string
   |  |  +--ro cookie_mask?      flow-cookie
   |  |  +--ro buffer_id?        uint32
   |  |  +--ro out_port?         uint64
   |  |  +--ro out_group?        uint32
   |  |  +--ro flags?            flow-mod-flags
   |  |  +--ro flow-name?        string
   |  |  +--ro installHw?        boolean
   |  |  +--ro barrier?          boolean
   |  |  +--ro strict?           boolean
   |  |  +--ro packet-count?     yang:counter64
   |  |  +--ro byte-count?       yang:counter64
   |  |  +--ro duration
   |  |     +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |  |     +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |  +--ro transaction-id?                 transaction-id
   +---n aggregate-flow-statistics-update    
      +--ro id?               node-id
      +--ro node-connector* [id]
      |  +--ro id    node-connector-id
      +--ro packet-count?     yang:counter64
      +--ro byte-count?       yang:counter64
      +--ro flow-count?       yang:counter32
      +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
      +--ro moreReplies?      boolean
module: opendaylight-flow-table-statistics
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/flow-node:table:
   +--rw flow-table-statistics
      +--rw active-flows?        yang:counter32
      +--rw packets-looked-up?   yang:counter64
      +--rw packets-matched?     yang:counter64
rpcs:
   +---x get-flow-tables-statistics    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w node?   node-ref
      +--ro output    
         +--ro flow-table-and-statistics-map* [table-id]
         |  +--ro table-id             table-types:table-id
         |  +--ro active-flows?        yang:counter32
         |  +--ro packets-looked-up?   yang:counter64
         |  +--ro packets-matched?     yang:counter64
         +--ro transaction-id?                  transaction-id
notifications:
   +---n flow-table-statistics-update    
      +--ro id?                              node-id
      +--ro node-connector* [id]
      |  +--ro id    node-connector-id
      +--ro flow-table-and-statistics-map* [table-id]
      |  +--ro table-id             table-types:table-id
      |  +--ro active-flows?        yang:counter32
      |  +--ro packets-looked-up?   yang:counter64
      |  +--ro packets-matched?     yang:counter64
      +--ro transaction-id?                  transaction-id
      +--ro moreReplies?                     boolean
module: opendaylight-group-statistics
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/fni:group:
   +--rw group-statistics
      +--rw group-id?       group-id
      +--rw ref-count?      yang:counter32
      +--rw packet-count?   yang:counter64
      +--rw byte-count?     yang:counter64
      +--rw duration
      |  +--rw second?       yang:counter32
      |  +--rw nanosecond?   yang:counter32
      +--rw buckets
         +--rw bucket-counter* [bucket-id]
            +--rw bucket-id       bucket-id
            +--rw packet-count?   yang:counter64
            +--rw byte-count?     yang:counter64
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/fni:group:
   +--rw group-desc
      +--rw group-type?       group-types
      +--rw group-id?         group-id
      +--rw group-name?       string
      +--rw container-name?   string
      +--rw barrier?          boolean
      +--rw buckets
         +--rw bucket* [bucket-id]
            +--rw bucket-id      bucket-id
            +--rw weight?        uint16
            +--rw watch_port?    uint32
            +--rw watch_group?   uint32
            +--rw action* [order]
               +--rw order                  int32
               +--rw (action)?
                  +--:(output-action-case)
                  |  +--rw output-action
                  |     +--rw output-node-connector?   inet:uri
                  |     +--rw max-length?              uint16
                  +--:(controller-action-case)
                  |  +--rw controller-action
                  |     +--rw max-length?   uint16
                  +--:(set-field-case)
                  |  +--rw set-field
                  |     +--rw in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
                  |     +--rw in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
                  |     +--rw metadata
                  |     |  +--rw metadata?        uint64
                  |     |  +--rw metadata-mask?   uint64
                  |     +--rw tunnel
                  |     |  +--rw tunnel-id?     uint64
                  |     |  +--rw tunnel-mask?   uint64
                  |     +--rw ethernet-match
                  |     |  +--rw ethernet-source!
                  |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |     |  +--rw ethernet-destination!
                  |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |     |  +--rw ethernet-type!
                  |     |     +--rw type    l2t:ether-type
                  |     +--rw vlan-match
                  |     |  +--rw vlan-id!
                  |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id-present?   boolean
                  |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
                  |     |  +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  |     +--rw ip-match
                  |     |  +--rw ip-protocol?   uint8
                  |     |  +--rw ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
                  |     |  +--rw ip-ecn?        uint8
                  |     |  +--rw ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
                  |     +--rw (layer-3-match)?
                  |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-label
                  |     |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |     |  |  |  +--rw flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-ext-header
                  |     |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
                  |     |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
                  |     |  +--:(arp-match)
                  |     |  |  +--rw arp-op?                         uint16
                  |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-hardware-address!
                  |     |  |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-hardware-address!
                  |     |  |     +--rw address    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |     +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
                  |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     +--rw (layer-4-match)?
                  |     |  +--:(udp-match)
                  |     |  |  +--rw udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |     |  |  +--rw udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
                  |     |  |  +--rw tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |     |  |  +--rw tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
                  |     |     +--rw sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
                  |     |     +--rw sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
                  |     +--rw icmpv4-match
                  |     |  +--rw icmpv4-type?   uint8
                  |     |  +--rw icmpv4-code?   uint8
                  |     +--rw icmpv6-match
                  |     |  +--rw icmpv6-type?   uint8
                  |     |  +--rw icmpv6-code?   uint8
                  |     +--rw protocol-match-fields
                  |     |  +--rw mpls-label?   uint32
                  |     |  +--rw mpls-tc?      uint8
                  |     |  +--rw mpls-bos?     uint8
                  |     |  +--rw pbb
                  |     |     +--rw pbb-isid?   uint32
                  |     |     +--rw pbb-mask?   uint32
                  |     +--rw tcp-flag-match
                  |        +--rw tcp-flag?   uint16
                  +--:(set-queue-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-queue-action
                  |     +--rw queue?      string
                  |     +--rw queue-id?   uint32
                  +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
                  |  +--rw pop-mpls-action
                  |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
                  +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-mpls-ttl-action
                  |     +--rw mpls-ttl?   uint8
                  +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-nw-ttl-action
                  |     +--rw nw-ttl?   uint8
                  +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
                  |  +--rw push-pbb-action
                  |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
                  +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
                  |  +--rw pop-pbb-action
                  +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
                  |  +--rw push-mpls-action
                  |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
                  +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
                  |  +--rw dec-mpls-ttl
                  +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
                  |  +--rw dec-nw-ttl
                  +--:(drop-action-case)
                  |  +--rw drop-action
                  +--:(flood-action-case)
                  |  +--rw flood-action
                  +--:(flood-all-action-case)
                  |  +--rw flood-all-action
                  +--:(hw-path-action-case)
                  |  +--rw hw-path-action
                  +--:(loopback-action-case)
                  |  +--rw loopback-action
                  +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
                  |  +--rw pop-vlan-action
                  +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
                  |  +--rw push-vlan-action
                  |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |     +--rw tag?             int32
                  |     +--rw pcp?             int32
                  |     +--rw cfi?             vlan-cfi
                  |     +--rw vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
                  +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
                  |  +--rw copy-ttl-out
                  +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
                  |  +--rw copy-ttl-in
                  +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-dl-dst-action
                  |     +--rw address?   yang:mac-address
                  +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-dl-src-action
                  |     +--rw address?   yang:mac-address
                  +--:(group-action-case)
                  |  +--rw group-action
                  |     +--rw group?      string
                  |     +--rw group-id?   uint32
                  +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-dl-type-action
                  |     +--rw dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
                  +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-next-hop-action
                  |     +--rw (address)?
                  |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-nw-dst-action
                  |     +--rw (address)?
                  |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-nw-src-action
                  |     +--rw (address)?
                  |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-nw-tos-action
                  |     +--rw tos?   int32
                  +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-tp-dst-action
                  |     +--rw port?   inet:port-number
                  +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-tp-src-action
                  |     +--rw port?   inet:port-number
                  +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-vlan-cfi-action
                  |     +--rw vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
                  +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-vlan-id-action
                  |     +--rw vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
                  +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-vlan-pcp-action
                  |     +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
                  |  +--rw strip-vlan-action
                  +--:(sw-path-action-case)
                     +--rw sw-path-action
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node:
   +--rw group-features
      +--rw group-types-supported*          identityref
      +--rw group-capabilities-supported*   identityref
      +--rw max-groups*                     uint32
      +--rw actions*                        uint32
rpcs:
   +---x get-all-group-statistics    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?   node-ref
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro group-stats* [group-id]
   |     |  +--ro group-id        group-id
   |     |  +--ro ref-count?      yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro packet-count?   yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro byte-count?     yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro duration
   |     |  |  +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |     |  |  +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro buckets
   |     |     +--ro bucket-counter* [bucket-id]
   |     |        +--ro bucket-id       bucket-id
   |     |        +--ro packet-count?   yang:counter64
   |     |        +--ro byte-count?     yang:counter64
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x get-group-statistics        
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?       node-ref
   |  |  +---w group-id?   group-types:group-id
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro group-stats* [group-id]
   |     |  +--ro group-id        group-id
   |     |  +--ro ref-count?      yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro packet-count?   yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro byte-count?     yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro duration
   |     |  |  +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |     |  |  +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro buckets
   |     |     +--ro bucket-counter* [bucket-id]
   |     |        +--ro bucket-id       bucket-id
   |     |        +--ro packet-count?   yang:counter64
   |     |        +--ro byte-count?     yang:counter64

   |     |           +--ro (action)?
   |     |              +--:(output-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro output-action
   |     |              |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |     |              |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
   |     |              +--:(controller-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro controller-action
   |     |              |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
   |     |              +--:(set-field-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro set-field

   |     |              |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |     |              |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64

   |     |              |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |              |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64

   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |              |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp

   |     |              |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |              |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8

   |     |              |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?

   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix

   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address

   |     |              |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |     |              |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |     |              |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |              |     |  +--:(arp-match)

   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix

   |     |              |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |              |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?

   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number

   |     |              |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
   |     |              |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
   |     |              |     |  +--ro pbb
   |     |              |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
   |     |              |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
   |     |              |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
   |     |              |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   |     |              +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro set-queue-action
   |     |              |     +--ro queue?      string
   |     |              |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
   |     |              +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
   |     |              |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |              +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action
   |     |              |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |     |              +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)

   |     |              +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro push-pbb-action
   |     |              |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |              +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro pop-pbb-action
   |     |              +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro push-mpls-action
   |     |              |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |              +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro dec-mpls-ttl
   |     |              +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro dec-nw-ttl

   |  +--ro id?               node-id

   +--:(inmemory-config-datastore-provider)
      +--rw inmemory-config-datastore-provider
         +--rw schema-service
         |  +--rw type?   service-type-ref
         |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
         +--rw max-data-change-executor-queue-size?   uint16
         +--rw max-data-change-executor-pool-size?    uint16
         +--rw max-data-change-listener-queue-size?   uint16
         +--rw max-data-store-executor-queue-size?    uint16
         +--rw debug-transactions?                    boolean

module: opendaylight-inventory
   +--rw nodes
      +--rw node* [id]
         +--rw id                node-id
         +--rw node-connector* [id]
            +--rw id    node-connector-id
notifications:
   x---n node-updated              
   |  +--ro node-ref?         node-ref
   |  +--ro id?               node-id
   |  +--ro node-connector* [id]
   |     +--ro id    node-connector-id
   x---n node-connector-updated    
   |  +--ro node-connector-ref?   node-connector-ref
   |  +--ro id?                   node-connector-id
   x---n node-removed              
   |  +--ro node-ref?   node-ref
   x---n node-connector-removed    
      +--ro node-connector-ref?   node-connector-ref

augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/flow-node:meter:
   +--rw meter-statistics
      +--rw meter-id?           meter-id
      +--rw flow-count?         yang:counter32
      +--rw packet-in-count?    yang:counter64
      +--rw byte-in-count?      yang:counter64
      +--rw duration
      |  +--rw second?       yang:counter32
      |  +--rw nanosecond?   yang:counter32
      +--rw meter-band-stats
         +--rw band-stat* [band-id]
            +--rw band-id              band-id
            +--rw packet-band-count?   yang:counter64
            +--rw byte-band-count?     yang:counter64
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/flow-node:meter:
   +--rw meter-config-stats
      +--rw flags?                meter-flags
      +--rw meter-id?             meter-id
      +--rw barrier?              boolean
      +--rw meter-name?           string
      +--rw container-name?       string
      +--rw meter-band-headers
         +--rw meter-band-header* [band-id]
            +--rw band-id                    band-id

               +--:(experimenter)
                  +--rw experimenter-rate?         uint32
                  +--rw experimenter-burst-size?   uint32
                  +--rw experimenter?              uint32

rpcs:
   +---x echo                 
   |  +---w input

   |  |  +--ro type?            identityref
   |  |  +--ro match-entries*
   |  |     +--ro oxm-class?         identityref
   |  |     +--ro oxm-match-field?   identityref
   |  |     +--ro has-mask?          boolean
   |  +--ro match-v10
   |     +--ro wildcards?     oft:flow-wildcards-v10
   |     +--ro nw-src-mask?   uint8
   |     +--ro nw-dst-mask?   uint8
   |     +--ro in-port?       uint16
   |     +--ro dl-src?        yang:mac-address
   |     +--ro dl-dst?        yang:mac-address

   |     +--ro dl-type?       uint16

   |     +--ro nw-dst?        inet:ipv4-address

   |     +--ro tp-dst?        uint16

   |  +--ro current-features-v10?      oft:port-features-v10
   |  +--ro advertised-features-v10?   oft:port-features-v10
   |  +--ro supported-features-v10?    oft:port-features-v10
   |  +--ro peer-features-v10?         oft:port-features-v10
   |  +--ro reason?                    oft:port-reason
   +---n multipart-reply-message    
      +--ro version?                          uint8
      +--ro xid?                              uint32
      +--ro type?                             oft:multipart-type
      +--ro flags?                            oft:multipart-request-flags
      +--ro (multipart-reply-body)?
         +--:(multipart-reply-desc-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-desc
         |     +--ro mfr_desc?     string
         |     +--ro hw_desc?      string
         |     +--ro sw_desc?      string
         |     +--ro serial_num?   string
         |     +--ro dp_desc?      string
         +--:(multipart-reply-flow-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-flow
         |     +--ro flow-stats*
         |        +--ro table-id?        uint8
         |        +--ro duration-sec?    uint32
         |        +--ro duration-nsec?   uint32
         |        +--ro priority?        uint16
         |        +--ro idle-timeout?    uint16
         |        +--ro hard-timeout?    uint16
         |        +--ro flags?           oft:flow-mod-flags
         |        +--ro cookie?          uint64
         |        +--ro packet-count?    uint64
         |        +--ro byte-count?      uint64
         |        +--ro match
         |        |  +--ro type?            identityref
         |        |  +--ro match-entries*
         |        |     +--ro oxm-class?         identityref
         |        |     +--ro oxm-match-field?   identityref
         |        |     +--ro has-mask?          boolean
         |        +--ro instruction*
         |        |  +--ro type?   identityref
         |        +--ro match-v10
         |        |  +--ro wildcards?     oft:flow-wildcards-v10
         |        |  +--ro nw-src-mask?   uint8
         |        |  +--ro nw-dst-mask?   uint8
         |        |  +--ro in-port?       uint16
         |        |  +--ro dl-src?        yang:mac-address
         |        |  +--ro dl-dst?        yang:mac-address
         |        |  +--ro dl-vlan?       uint16
         |        |  +--ro dl-vlan-pcp?   uint8
         |        |  +--ro dl-type?       uint16
         |        |  +--ro nw-tos?        uint8
         |        |  +--ro nw-proto?      uint8
         |        |  +--ro nw-src?        inet:ipv4-address
         |        |  +--ro nw-dst?        inet:ipv4-address
         |        |  +--ro tp-src?        uint16
         |        |  +--ro tp-dst?        uint16
         |        +--ro action*
         |           +--ro type?   identityref
         +--:(multipart-reply-aggregate-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-aggregate
         |     +--ro packet-count?   uint64
         |     +--ro byte-count?     uint64
         |     +--ro flow-count?     uint32
         +--:(multipart-reply-table-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-table
         |     +--ro table-stats*
         |        +--ro table-id?        uint8
         |        +--ro active-count?    uint32
         |        +--ro lookup-count?    uint64
         |        +--ro matched-count?   uint64
         |        +--ro name?            string
         |        +--ro wildcards?       oft:flow-wildcards-v10
         |        +--ro nw-src-mask?     uint8
         |        +--ro nw-dst-mask?     uint8
         |        +--ro max-entries?     uint32
         +--:(multipart-reply-port-stats-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-port-stats
         |     +--ro port-stats*
         |        +--ro port-no?         uint32
         |        +--ro rx-packets?      uint64
         |        +--ro tx-packets?      uint64
         |        +--ro rx-bytes?        uint64
         |        +--ro tx-bytes?        uint64
         |        +--ro rx-dropped?      uint64
         |        +--ro tx-dropped?      uint64
         |        +--ro rx-errors?       uint64
         |        +--ro tx-errors?       uint64
         |        +--ro rx-frame-err?    uint64
         |        +--ro rx-over-err?     uint64
         |        +--ro rx-crc-err?      uint64
         |        +--ro collisions?      uint64
         |        +--ro duration-sec?    uint32
         |        +--ro duration-nsec?   uint32
         +--:(multipart-reply-queue-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-queue
         |     +--ro queue-stats*
         |        +--ro port-no?         uint32
         |        +--ro queue-id?        uint32
         |        +--ro tx-bytes?        uint64
         |        +--ro tx-packets?      uint64
         |        +--ro tx-errors?       uint64
         |        +--ro duration-sec?    uint32
         |        +--ro duration-nsec?   uint32
         +--:(multipart-reply-group-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-group
         |     +--ro group-stats*
         |        +--ro group-id?        oft:group-id
         |        +--ro ref-count?       uint32
         |        +--ro packet-count?    uint64
         |        +--ro byte-count?      uint64
         |        +--ro duration-sec?    uint32
         |        +--ro duration-nsec?   uint32
         |        +--ro bucket-stats*
         |           +--ro packet-count?   uint64
         |           +--ro byte-count?     uint64
         +--:(multipart-reply-group-desc-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-group-desc
         |     +--ro group-desc*
         |        +--ro type?           oft:group-type
         |        +--ro group-id?       oft:group-id
         |        +--ro buckets-list*
         |           +--ro weight?        uint16
         |           +--ro watch-port?    oft:port-number
         |           +--ro watch-group?   uint32
         |           +--ro action*
         |              +--ro type?   identityref
         +--:(multipart-reply-group-features-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-group-features
         |     +--ro types?            oft:group-types
         |     +--ro capabilities?     oft:group-capabilities
         |     +--ro max_groups*       uint32
         |     +--ro actions-bitmap*   oft:action-type
         +--:(multipart-reply-meter-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-meter
         |     +--ro meter-stats*
         |        +--ro meter-id?           oft:meter-id
         |        +--ro flow-count?         uint32
         |        +--ro packet-in-count?    uint64
         |        +--ro byte-in-count?      uint64
         |        +--ro duration-sec?       uint32
         |        +--ro duration-nsec?      uint32
         |        +--ro meter-band-stats*
         |           +--ro packet-band-count?   uint64
         |           +--ro byte-band-count?     uint64
         +--:(multipart-reply-meter-config-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-meter-config
         |     +--ro meter-config*
         |        +--ro flags?      oft:meter-flags
         |        +--ro meter-id?   oft:meter-id
         |        +--ro bands*
         |           +--ro (meter-band)?
         |              +--:(meter-band-drop-case)
         |              |  +--ro meter-band-drop
         |              |     +--ro type?         oft:meter-band-type
         |              |     +--ro rate?         uint32
         |              |     +--ro burst-size?   uint32
         |              +--:(meter-band-dscp-remark-case)
         |              |  +--ro meter-band-dscp-remark
         |              |     +--ro type?         oft:meter-band-type
         |              |     +--ro rate?         uint32
         |              |     +--ro burst-size?   uint32
         |              |     +--ro prec-level?   uint8
         |              +--:(meter-band-experimenter-case)
         |                 +--ro meter-band-experimenter
         |                    +--ro type?         oft:meter-band-type
         |                    +--ro rate?         uint32
         |                    +--ro burst-size?   uint32
         +--:(multipart-reply-meter-features-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-meter-features
         |     +--ro max-meter?      uint32
         |     +--ro band-types?     oft:meter-band-type-bitmap
         |     +--ro capabilities?   oft:meter-flags
         |     +--ro max-bands?      uint8
         |     +--ro max-color?      uint8
         +--:(multipart-reply-table-features-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-table-features
         |     +--ro table-features*
         |        +--ro table-id?                   uint8
         |        +--ro name?                       string
         |        +--ro metadata-match?             binary
         |        +--ro metadata-write?             binary
         |        +--ro config?                     oft:table-config
         |        +--ro max-entries?                uint32
         |        +--ro table-feature-properties*
         |           +--ro type?   oft:table-features-prop-type
         +--:(multipart-reply-port-desc-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-port-desc
         |     +--ro ports*
         |        +--ro port-no?                   uint32
         |        +--ro hw-addr?                   yang:mac-address
         |        +--ro name?                      string
         |        +--ro config?                    oft:port-config
         |        +--ro state?                     oft:port-state
         |        +--ro current-features?          oft:port-features
         |        +--ro advertised-features?       oft:port-features
         |        +--ro supported-features?        oft:port-features
         |        +--ro peer-features?             oft:port-features
         |        +--ro curr-speed?                uint32
         |        +--ro max-speed?                 uint32
         |        +--ro config-v10?                oft:port-config-v10
         |        +--ro state-v10?                 oft:port-state-v10
         |        +--ro current-features-v10?      oft:port-features-v10
         |        +--ro advertised-features-v10?   oft:port-features-v10
         |        +--ro supported-features-v10?    oft:port-features-v10
         |        +--ro peer-features-v10?         oft:port-features-v10
         +--:(multipart-reply-experimenter-case)
            +--ro multipart-reply-experimenter
module: openflow-provider-impl
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(openflow-provider-impl)
   |  +--rw binding-aware-broker
   |  |  +--rw type    service-type-ref
   |  |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
   |  +--rw openflow-switch-connection-provider*
   |     +--rw type    service-type-ref
   |     +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
   +--:(msg-spy-service-impl)
      +--rw openflow-plugin-provider
         +--rw type    service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name

   +--:(msg-spy-service-impl)
      +--ro msgStatistics?   string

         +--ro result?   string
module: openflow-switch-connection-provider-impl

      |  +--rw truststore-type?        of-config:keystore-type

      |  +--rw truststore-password?    string
      +--rw threads
         +--rw boss-threads?     uint16
         +--rw worker-threads?   uint16
