module: packet-handler-impl
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(packet-handler-impl)
      +--rw notification-service
         +--rw type    service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
module: packet-processing
rpcs:
   +---x transmit-packet    
      +---w input     
         +---w node?                node-ref
         +---w connection-cookie?   connection-cookie
         +---w egress?              inv:node-connector-ref
         +---w buffer-id?           uint32
         +---w ingress?             inv:node-connector-ref
         +---w payload?             binary
         +---w action* [order]
            +---w order                  int32
            +---w (action)?
               +--:(output-action-case)
               |  +---w output-action
               |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
               |     +---w max-length?              uint16
               +--:(controller-action-case)
               |  +---w controller-action
               |     +---w max-length?   uint16
               +--:(set-field-case)
               |  +---w set-field
               |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
               |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
               |     +---w metadata
               |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
               |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
               |     +---w tunnel
               |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
               |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
               |     +---w ethernet-match
               |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
               |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
               |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
               |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
               |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
               |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
               |     +---w vlan-match
               |     |  +---w vlan-id!
               |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
               |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
               |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
               |     +---w ip-match
               |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
               |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
               |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
               |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
               |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
               |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
               |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
               |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
               |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
               |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
               |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
               |     |  +--:(arp-match)
               |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
               |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
               |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
               |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
               |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
               |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
               |     |  +--:(udp-match)
               |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
               |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
               |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
               |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
               |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
               |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
               |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
               |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
               |     +---w icmpv4-match
               |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
               |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
               |     +---w icmpv6-match
               |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
               |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
               |     +---w protocol-match-fields
               |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
               |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
               |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
               |     |  +---w pbb
               |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
               |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
               |     +---w tcp-flag-match
               |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
               +--:(set-queue-action-case)
               |  +---w set-queue-action
               |     +---w queue?      string
               |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
               +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
               |  +---w pop-mpls-action
               |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
               +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
               |  +---w set-mpls-ttl-action
               |     +---w mpls-ttl?   uint8
               +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
               |  +---w set-nw-ttl-action
               |     +---w nw-ttl?   uint8
               +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
               |  +---w push-pbb-action
               |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
               +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
               |  +---w pop-pbb-action
               +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
               |  +---w push-mpls-action
               |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
               +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
               |  +---w dec-mpls-ttl
               +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
               |  +---w dec-nw-ttl
               +--:(drop-action-case)
               |  +---w drop-action
               +--:(flood-action-case)
               |  +---w flood-action
               +--:(flood-all-action-case)
               |  +---w flood-all-action
               +--:(hw-path-action-case)
               |  +---w hw-path-action
               +--:(loopback-action-case)
               |  +---w loopback-action
               +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
               |  +---w pop-vlan-action
               +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
               |  +---w push-vlan-action
               |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
               |     +---w tag?             int32
               |     +---w pcp?             int32
               |     +---w cfi?             vlan-cfi
               |     +---w vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
               +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
               |  +---w copy-ttl-out
               +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
               |  +---w copy-ttl-in
               +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
               |  +---w set-dl-dst-action
               |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
               +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
               |  +---w set-dl-src-action
               |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
               +--:(group-action-case)
               |  +---w group-action
               |     +---w group?      string
               |     +---w group-id?   uint32
               +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
               |  +---w set-dl-type-action
               |     +---w dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
               +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
               |  +---w set-next-hop-action
               |     +---w (address)?
               |        +--:(ipv4)
               |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
               |        +--:(ipv6)
               |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
               +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
               |  +---w set-nw-dst-action
               |     +---w (address)?
               |        +--:(ipv4)
               |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
               |        +--:(ipv6)
               |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
               +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
               |  +---w set-nw-src-action
               |     +---w (address)?
               |        +--:(ipv4)
               |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
               |        +--:(ipv6)
               |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
               +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
               |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
               |     +---w tos?   int32
               +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
               |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
               |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
               +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
               |  +---w set-tp-src-action
               |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
               +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
               |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
               |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
               +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
               |  +---w set-vlan-id-action
               |     +---w vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
               +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
               |  +---w set-vlan-pcp-action
               |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
               +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
               |  +---w strip-vlan-action
               +--:(sw-path-action-case)
                  +---w sw-path-action
notifications:
   +---n packet-received    
      +--ro connection-cookie?   connection-cookie
      +--ro flow-cookie?         flow-type:flow-cookie
      +--ro table-id?            table-type:table-id
      +--ro packet-in-reason?    identityref
      +--ro match
      |  +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |  +--ro metadata
      |  |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
      |  |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  +--ro tunnel
      |  |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
      |  |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  +--ro ethernet-match
      |  |  +--ro ethernet-source!
      |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
      |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  +--ro ethernet-type!
      |  |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
      |  +--ro vlan-match
      |  |  +--ro vlan-id!
      |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |  |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  +--ro ip-match
      |  |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
      |  |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  +--ro (layer-3-match)?
      |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
      |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
      |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |  |  +--:(arp-match)
      |  |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
      |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
      |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
      |  |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  +--ro (layer-4-match)?
      |  |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |  |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |  |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |  |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |  +--ro icmpv4-match
      |  |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |  |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |  +--ro icmpv6-match
      |  |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |  |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |  +--ro protocol-match-fields
      |  |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
      |  |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
      |  |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
      |  |  +--ro pbb
      |  |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
      |  |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  +--ro tcp-flag-match
      |     +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
      +--ro ingress?             inv:node-connector-ref
      +--ro payload?             binary
module: protocol-framework
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(never-reconnect-strategy-factory)
      +--rw timeout     int32
      +--rw executor
         +--rw type    service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(reconnect-immediately-strategy-factory)
      +--rw reconnect-timeout     int32
      +--rw reconnect-executor
         +--rw type    service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(timed-reconnect-strategy-factory)
      +--rw deadline?                   int64
      +--rw max-attempts                int64
      +--rw max-sleep                   int64
      +--rw min-sleep                   int64
      +--rw sleep-factor                decimal64
      +--rw connect-time                int32
      +--rw timed-reconnect-executor
         +--rw type    service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
module: sal-flow
rpcs:
   +---x add-flow       
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w transaction-uri?   inet:uri
   |  |  +---w flow-ref?          types:flow-ref

   |  |  |  +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |  +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-id-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w strip-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(apply-actions-case)
   |  |  |        |  +---w apply-actions
   |  |  |        |     +---w action* [order]
   |  |  |        |        +---w order                  int32
   |  |  |        |        +---w (action)?
   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w output-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w controller-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-field
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w metadata
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tunnel
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ip-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w pbb
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-queue-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w pop-mpls-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w pop-pbb-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tag?             int32

   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w strip-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(clear-actions-case)
   |  |  |        |  +---w clear-actions
   |  |  |        |     +---w action* [order]
   |  |  |        |        +---w order                  int32
   |  |  |        |        +---w (action)?
   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w output-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w controller-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-field
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w metadata
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tunnel
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-match

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ip-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w pbb
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-queue-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w pop-mpls-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-mpls-ttl-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-ttl-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w nw-ttl?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w push-pbb-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w pop-pbb-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w push-mpls-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w dec-mpls-ttl
   |  |  |        |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w dec-nw-ttl
   |  |  |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w drop-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(flood-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w flood-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w flood-all-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w hw-path-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w loopback-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w pop-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w push-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tag?             int32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w pcp?             int32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-out
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-in
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(group-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w group-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w group?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w group-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-type-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-next-hop-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w strip-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(meter-case)
   |  |  |           +---w meter
   |  |  |              +---w meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |  |  +---w priority?          uint16
   |  |  +---w idle-timeout?      uint16
   |  |  +---w hard-timeout?      uint16
   |  |  +---w cookie?            flow-cookie
   |  |  +---w table_id?          uint8
   |  |  +---w container-name?    string
   |  |  +---w cookie_mask?       flow-cookie
   |  |  +---w buffer_id?         uint32
   |  |  +---w out_port?          uint64
   |  |  +---w out_group?         uint32
   |  |  +---w flags?             flow-mod-flags
   |  |  +---w flow-name?         string
   |  |  +---w installHw?         boolean
   |  |  +---w barrier?           boolean
   |  |  +---w strict?            boolean
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x remove-flow    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w transaction-uri?   inet:uri
   |  |  +---w flow-ref?          types:flow-ref
   |  |  +---w node?              node-ref
   |  |  +---w flow-table?        flow-table-ref
   |  |  +---w match
   |  |  |  +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |  +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |  +---w metadata
   |  |  |  |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |  |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |  +---w tunnel
   |  |  |  |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |  |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |  +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |  |  |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |  +---w vlan-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |  +---w ip-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |  +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)

   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-label

   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |  |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!

   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)

   |  |  |  |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tcp-match)

   |  |  +---w instructions

   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32

   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w push-pbb-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w pop-pbb-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w push-mpls-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w dec-mpls-ttl
   |  |  |        |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w dec-nw-ttl
   |  |  |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w drop-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(flood-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w flood-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w flood-all-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w hw-path-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w loopback-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w pop-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w push-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tag?             int32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w pcp?             int32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-out
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-in
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(group-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w group-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w group?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w group-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(apply-actions-case)

   |  |  |        |     +---w action* [order]
   |  |  |        |        +---w order                  int32
   |  |  |        |        +---w (action)?
   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w output-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-field
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w metadata
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tunnel
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ip-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w pbb
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-queue-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32

   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(group-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w group?      string

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(clear-actions-case)
   |  |  |        |  +---w clear-actions
   |  |  |        |     +---w action* [order]
   |  |  |        |        +---w order                  int32
   |  |  |        |        +---w (action)?
   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w output-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w controller-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-field
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w metadata
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tunnel
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ip-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w pbb
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-queue-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w pop-mpls-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-mpls-ttl-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w nw-ttl?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w push-mpls-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w dec-mpls-ttl
   |  |  |        |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w dec-nw-ttl
   |  |  |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(flood-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w flood-action

   |  |  |        |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w hw-path-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w loopback-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w pop-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w push-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tag?             int32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w pcp?             int32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-out
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-in
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(group-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w group?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w group-id?   uint32

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix

   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w strip-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(meter-case)
   |  |  |           +---w meter
   |  |  |              +---w meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |  |  +---w priority?          uint16
   |  |  +---w idle-timeout?      uint16
   |  |  +---w hard-timeout?      uint16
   |  |  +---w cookie?            flow-cookie
   |  |  +---w table_id?          uint8
   |  |  +---w container-name?    string
   |  |  +---w cookie_mask?       flow-cookie
   |  |  +---w buffer_id?         uint32
   |  |  +---w out_port?          uint64
   |  |  +---w out_group?         uint32
   |  |  +---w flags?             flow-mod-flags
   |  |  +---w flow-name?         string
   |  |  +---w installHw?         boolean
   |  |  +---w barrier?           boolean
   |  |  +---w strict?            boolean
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x update-flow    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w transaction-uri?   inet:uri
      |  +---w flow-ref?          types:flow-ref
      |  +---w node?              node-ref
      |  +---w original-flow
      |  |  +---w match
      |  |  |  +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  |  |  +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

      |  |  |  |  +---w metadata?        uint64
      |  |  |  |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  |  |  +---w tunnel
      |  |  |  |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
      |  |  |  |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |  |  +---w ethernet-match
      |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-destination!

      |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-type!

      |  |  |  +---w vlan-match

      |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |  |  +---w ip-match

      |  |  |  |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |  |  |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |  |  |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |  |  +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix

      |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address

      |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label

      |  |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16

      |  |  |  |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number

      |  |  |        |           |     +---w ip-match

      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8

      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w pbb
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
      |  |  |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32

      |  |  |        |        +---w (action)?
      |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!

      |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
