   |  |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |  |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |  |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |           |     +--ro icmpv4-match
   |  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |           |     +--ro icmpv6-match
   |  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |           |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
   |  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |           |     |  +--ro pbb
   |  |           |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
   |  |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-queue-action
   |  |           |     +--ro queue?      string
   |  |           |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
   |  |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
   |  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action
   |  |           |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |  |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-nw-ttl-action
   |  |           |     +--ro nw-ttl?   uint8
   |  |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro push-pbb-action
   |  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro pop-pbb-action
   |  |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro push-mpls-action
   |  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro dec-mpls-ttl
   |  |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro dec-nw-ttl
   |  |           +--:(drop-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro drop-action
   |  |           +--:(flood-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro flood-action
   |  |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro flood-all-action
   |  |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro hw-path-action
   |  |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro loopback-action
   |  |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro pop-vlan-action
   |  |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro push-vlan-action
   |  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           |     +--ro tag?             int32
   |  |           |     +--ro pcp?             int32
   |  |           |     +--ro cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |           |     +--ro vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-out
   |  |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-in
   |  |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-dl-dst-action
   |  |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-dl-src-action
   |  |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |           +--:(group-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro group-action
   |  |           |     +--ro group?      string
   |  |           |     +--ro group-id?   uint32
   |  |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-dl-type-action
   |  |           |     +--ro dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-next-hop-action
   |  |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)

   |  |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)

   |  |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)

   |  |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |  |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |  |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |  |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)

   |  |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |  |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)

   |  |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |  |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |  +--ro transaction-id?    transaction-id
   +---n group-updated    
   |  +--ro transaction-uri?   inet:uri
   |  +--ro group-ref?         group-type:group-ref
   |  +--ro node?              node-ref
   |  +--ro group-type?        group-types
   |  +--ro group-id?          group-id
   |  +--ro group-name?        string
   |  +--ro container-name?    string
   |  +--ro barrier?           boolean
   |  +--ro buckets
   |  |  +--ro bucket* [bucket-id]
   |  |     +--ro bucket-id      bucket-id
   |  |     +--ro weight?        uint16
   |  |     +--ro watch_port?    uint32
   |  |     +--ro watch_group?   uint32
   |  |     +--ro action* [order]
   |  |        +--ro order                  int32
   |  |        +--ro (action)?
   |  |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro output-action
   |  |           |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |           |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
   |  |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro controller-action
   |  |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
   |  |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-field
   |  |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |     +--ro metadata
   |  |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |  |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |     +--ro tunnel
   |  |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
   |  |           |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |           |     +--ro vlan-match
   |  |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           |     +--ro ip-match
   |  |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |  |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |  |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |  |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |  |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number

   |  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8

   |  |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32

   |  |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-queue-action

   |  |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
   |  |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |  |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)

   |  |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |  |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)

   |  |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)

   |  |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)

   |  |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |  |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |  +--ro transaction-id?    transaction-id
   +---n group-removed    
      +--ro transaction-uri?   inet:uri
      +--ro group-ref?         group-type:group-ref
      +--ro node?              node-ref
      +--ro group-type?        group-types
      +--ro group-id?          group-id
      +--ro group-name?        string
      +--ro container-name?    string
      +--ro barrier?           boolean
      +--ro buckets
      |  +--ro bucket* [bucket-id]
      |     +--ro bucket-id      bucket-id
      |     +--ro weight?        uint16
      |     +--ro watch_port?    uint32
      |     +--ro watch_group?   uint32
      |     +--ro action* [order]
      |        +--ro order                  int32
      |        +--ro (action)?
      |           +--:(output-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro output-action
      |           |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
      |           |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
      |           +--:(controller-action-case)

      |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16

      |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

      |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
      |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
      |           |     +--ro tunnel
      |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
      |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
      |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
      |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
      |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
      |           |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
      |           |     +--ro vlan-match
      |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
      |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |           |     +--ro ip-match
      |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
      |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
      |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
      |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
      |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
      |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
      |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
      |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
      |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
      |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
      |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |           |     +--ro icmpv4-match
      |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |           |     +--ro icmpv6-match
      |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |           |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
      |           |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
      |           |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
      |           |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
      |           |     |  +--ro pbb
      |           |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
      |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
      |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
      |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
      |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-queue-action
      |           |     +--ro queue?      string
      |           |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
      |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
      |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
      |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action
      |           |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
      |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-nw-ttl-action
      |           |     +--ro nw-ttl?   uint8
      |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro push-pbb-action
      |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
      |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro pop-pbb-action
      |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro push-mpls-action
      |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
      |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
      |           |  +--ro dec-mpls-ttl
      |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
      |           |  +--ro dec-nw-ttl
      |           +--:(drop-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro drop-action
      |           +--:(flood-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro flood-action
      |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro flood-all-action
      |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro hw-path-action
      |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro loopback-action
      |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro pop-vlan-action
      |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro push-vlan-action
      |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
      |           |     +--ro tag?             int32
      |           |     +--ro pcp?             int32
      |           |     +--ro cfi?             vlan-cfi
      |           |     +--ro vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
      |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
      |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-out
      |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
      |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-in
      |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-dl-dst-action
      |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
      |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-dl-src-action
      |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
      |           +--:(group-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro group-action
      |           |     +--ro group?      string
      |           |     +--ro group-id?   uint32
      |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-dl-type-action
      |           |     +--ro dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
      |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-next-hop-action
      |           |     +--ro (address)?
      |           |        +--:(ipv4)
      |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |           |        +--:(ipv6)
      |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-nw-dst-action
      |           |     +--ro (address)?
      |           |        +--:(ipv4)
      |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |           |        +--:(ipv6)
      |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-nw-src-action
      |           |     +--ro (address)?
      |           |        +--:(ipv4)
      |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |           |        +--:(ipv6)
      |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
      |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
      |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
      |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
      |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
      |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
      |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
      |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
      |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
      |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
      |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
      |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
      |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
      |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
      |              +--ro sw-path-action
      +--ro transaction-id?    transaction-id
module: sal-meter
rpcs:
   +---x add-meter       
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w transaction-uri?      inet:uri
   |  |  +---w meter-ref?            meter-type:meter-ref
   |  |  +---w node?                 node-ref
   |  |  +---w flags?                meter-flags
   |  |  +---w meter-id?             meter-id
   |  |  +---w barrier?              boolean
   |  |  +---w meter-name?           string
   |  |  +---w container-name?       string
   |  |  +---w meter-band-headers
   |  |     +---w meter-band-header* [band-id]
   |  |        +---w band-id                    band-id
   |  |        +---w meter-band-types
   |  |        |  +---w flags?   meter-band-type
   |  |        +---w band-rate?                 uint32
   |  |        +---w band-burst-size?           uint32
   |  |        +---w (band-type)?
   |  |           +--:(drop)
   |  |           |  +---w drop-rate?                 uint32
   |  |           |  +---w drop-burst-size?           uint32
   |  |           +--:(dscp-remark)
   |  |           |  +---w dscp-remark-rate?          uint32
   |  |           |  +---w dscp-remark-burst-size?    uint32
   |  |           |  +---w perc_level?                uint8
   |  |           +--:(experimenter)
   |  |              +---w experimenter-rate?         uint32
   |  |              +---w experimenter-burst-size?   uint32
   |  |              +---w experimenter?              uint32
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x remove-meter    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w transaction-uri?      inet:uri
   |  |  +---w meter-ref?            meter-type:meter-ref
   |  |  +---w node?                 node-ref
   |  |  +---w flags?                meter-flags
   |  |  +---w meter-id?             meter-id
   |  |  +---w barrier?              boolean
   |  |  +---w meter-name?           string
   |  |  +---w container-name?       string
   |  |  +---w meter-band-headers
   |  |     +---w meter-band-header* [band-id]
   |  |        +---w band-id                    band-id
   |  |        +---w meter-band-types
   |  |        |  +---w flags?   meter-band-type
   |  |        +---w band-rate?                 uint32
   |  |        +---w band-burst-size?           uint32
   |  |        +---w (band-type)?
   |  |           +--:(drop)
   |  |           |  +---w drop-rate?                 uint32
   |  |           |  +---w drop-burst-size?           uint32
   |  |           +--:(dscp-remark)
   |  |           |  +---w dscp-remark-rate?          uint32
   |  |           |  +---w dscp-remark-burst-size?    uint32
   |  |           |  +---w perc_level?                uint8
   |  |           +--:(experimenter)
   |  |              +---w experimenter-rate?         uint32
   |  |              +---w experimenter-burst-size?   uint32
   |  |              +---w experimenter?              uint32
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x update-meter    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w transaction-uri?   inet:uri
      |  +---w meter-ref?         meter-type:meter-ref
      |  +---w node?              node-ref
      |  +---w original-meter
      |  |  +---w flags?                meter-flags
      |  |  +---w meter-id?             meter-id
      |  |  +---w barrier?              boolean
      |  |  +---w meter-name?           string
      |  |  +---w container-name?       string
      |  |  +---w meter-band-headers
      |  |     +---w meter-band-header* [band-id]
      |  |        +---w band-id                    band-id
      |  |        +---w meter-band-types
      |  |        |  +---w flags?   meter-band-type
      |  |        +---w band-rate?                 uint32
      |  |        +---w band-burst-size?           uint32
      |  |        +---w (band-type)?
      |  |           +--:(drop)
      |  |           |  +---w drop-rate?                 uint32
      |  |           |  +---w drop-burst-size?           uint32
      |  |           +--:(dscp-remark)
      |  |           |  +---w dscp-remark-rate?          uint32
      |  |           |  +---w dscp-remark-burst-size?    uint32
      |  |           |  +---w perc_level?                uint8
      |  |           +--:(experimenter)
      |  |              +---w experimenter-rate?         uint32
      |  |              +---w experimenter-burst-size?   uint32
      |  |              +---w experimenter?              uint32
      |  +---w updated-meter
      |     +---w flags?                meter-flags
      |     +---w meter-id?             meter-id
      |     +---w barrier?              boolean
      |     +---w meter-name?           string
      |     +---w container-name?       string
      |     +---w meter-band-headers
      |        +---w meter-band-header* [band-id]
      |           +---w band-id                    band-id
      |           +---w meter-band-types
      |           |  +---w flags?   meter-band-type
      |           +---w band-rate?                 uint32
      |           +---w band-burst-size?           uint32
      |           +---w (band-type)?
      |              +--:(drop)
      |              |  +---w drop-rate?                 uint32
      |              |  +---w drop-burst-size?           uint32
      |              +--:(dscp-remark)
      |              |  +---w dscp-remark-rate?          uint32
      |              |  +---w dscp-remark-burst-size?    uint32
      |              |  +---w perc_level?                uint8
      |              +--:(experimenter)
      |                 +---w experimenter-rate?         uint32
      |                 +---w experimenter-burst-size?   uint32
      |                 +---w experimenter?              uint32
      +--ro output    
         +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id

module: sal-port
rpcs:
   +---x update-port    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w node?             node-ref
      |  +---w original-port
      |  |  +---w port
      |  |     +---w port* [port-mod-order]
      |  |        +---w port-mod-order         uint32
      |  |        +---w port-number?           union
      |  |        +---w hardware-address?      yang:mac-address
      |  |        +---w configuration?         port-config
      |  |        +---w advertised-features?   port-features
      |  |        +---w mask?                  port-config
      |  |        +---w container-name?        string
      |  |        +---w port-name?             string
      |  |        +---w barrier?               boolean
      |  +---w updated-port
      |  |  +---w port
      |  |     +---w port* [port-mod-order]
      |  |        +---w port-mod-order         uint32
      |  |        +---w port-number?           union
      |  |        +---w hardware-address?      yang:mac-address
      |  |        +---w configuration?         port-config
      |  |        +---w advertised-features?   port-features
      |  |        +---w mask?                  port-config
      |  |        +---w container-name?        string
      |  |        +---w port-name?             string
      |  |        +---w barrier?               boolean
      |  +---w transaction-id?   transaction-id
      +--ro output    
         +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
notifications:
   +---n port-updated    
   |  +--ro node?             node-ref
   |  +--ro original-port
   |  |  +--ro port
   |  |     +--ro port* [port-mod-order]
   |  |        +--ro port-mod-order         uint32
   |  |        +--ro port-number?           union
   |  |        +--ro hardware-address?      yang:mac-address
   |  |        +--ro configuration?         port-config
   |  |        +--ro advertised-features?   port-features
   |  |        +--ro mask?                  port-config
   |  |        +--ro container-name?        string
   |  |        +--ro port-name?             string
   |  |        +--ro barrier?               boolean
   |  +--ro updated-port
   |  |  +--ro port
   |  |     +--ro port* [port-mod-order]
   |  |        +--ro port-mod-order         uint32
   |  |        +--ro port-number?           union
   |  |        +--ro hardware-address?      yang:mac-address
   |  |        +--ro configuration?         port-config
   |  |        +--ro advertised-features?   port-features
   |  |        +--ro mask?                  port-config
   |  |        +--ro container-name?        string
   |  |        +--ro port-name?             string
   |  |        +--ro barrier?               boolean
   |  +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---n port-removed    
      +--ro node?                  node-ref
      +--ro reason?                port-reason
      +--ro port-number?           union
      +--ro hardware-address?      yang:mac-address
      +--ro configuration?         port-config
      +--ro advertised-features?   port-features
      +--ro name?                  string
      +--ro state
      |  +--ro link-down?   boolean
      |  +--ro blocked?     boolean
      |  +--ro live?        boolean
      +--ro current-feature?       port-features
      +--ro supported?             port-features
      +--ro peer-features?         port-features
      +--ro current-speed?         uint32
      +--ro maximum-speed?         uint32
      +--ro queue* [queue-id]
         +--ro queue-id    queue-id
         +--ro port?       uint32
         +--ro property?   uint16

      +--ro output    
         +--ro queue-id?   queue-id
         +--ro port?       uint32
         +--ro property?   uint16

      +--ro port?       uint32
      +--ro property?   uint16
module: sal-remote-augment
augment /salrmt:create-data-change-event-subscription/salrmt:input:
   +---- datastore?   enumeration
   +---- scope?       enumeration

rpcs:

   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w path?   instance-identifier
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro stream-name?   string
   +---x create-notification-stream               
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w notifications*   q-name
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro notification-stream-identifier?   string
   +---x begin-transaction                        
      +--ro output    
         +--ro data-modification-transaction

      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match

      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64

      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w ethernet-match
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w vlan-match
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w ip-match
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address

      |  |              |           |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)

      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w pbb
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  |              |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
      |  |              |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
      |  |              |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-queue-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w queue?      string
      |  |              |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
      |  |              |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)

      |  |              |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
      |  |              |           |     +---w tag?             int32
      |  |              |           |     +---w pcp?             int32

      |  |              |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)

      |  |              |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |           |     +---w ethernet-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address

      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp

      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |              |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?

      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix

      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label

      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label

      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header

      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)

      |  |              |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix

      |  |              |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |              |           |     +---w ip-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |              |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

      |  |              |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w pbb
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  |              |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
      |  |              |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
      |  |              |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)

      |  |              |     +---w action* [order]
      |  |              |        +---w order                  int32
      |  |              |        +---w (action)?
      |  |              |           +--:(output-action-case)

      |  |              |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
      |  |              |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
      |  |              |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-vlan-id-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
      |  |              |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-vlan-pcp-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |              |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w strip-vlan-action
      |  |              |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
      |  |              |              +---w sw-path-action
      |  |              +--:(match)
      |  |              |  +---w match-setfield
      |  |              |     +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |              |        +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |              |        +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  |              +--:(wildcards)
      |  |              |  +---w wildcard-setfield
      |  |              |     +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |              |        +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |              |        +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  |              +--:(write-setfield)
      |  |              |  +---w write-setfield
      |  |              |     +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |              |        +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |              |        +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  |              +--:(write-setfield-miss)
      |  |              |  +---w write-setfield-miss
      |  |              |     +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |              |        +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |              |        +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  |              +--:(apply-setfield)
      |  |              |  +---w apply-setfield
      |  |              |     +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |              |        +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |              |        +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  |              +--:(apply-setfield-miss)
      |  |                 +---w apply-setfield-miss
      |  |                    +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |                       +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |                       +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  +---w updated-table
      |  |  +---w table-features* [table-id]
      |  |     +---w table-id            uint8
      |  |     +---w name?               string
      |  |     +---w metadata-match?     uint64
      |  |     +---w metadata-write?     uint64
      |  |     +---w max-entries?        uint32
      |  |     +---w config?             table-config
      |  |     +---w table-properties
      |  |        +---w table-feature-properties* [order]
      |  |           +---w order                  int32
      |  |           +---w (table-feature-prop-type)?
      |  |              +--:(instructions)
      |  |              |  +---w instructions
      |  |              |     +---w instruction* [order]
      |  |              |        +---w order             int32
      |  |              |        +---w (instruction)?
      |  |              |           +--:(go-to-table-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w go-to-table
      |  |              |           |     +---w table_id?   uint8
      |  |              |           +--:(write-metadata-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w write-metadata
      |  |              |           |     +---w metadata?        uint64
      |  |              |           |     +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |           +--:(write-actions-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w write-actions
      |  |              |           |     +---w action* [order]
      |  |              |           |        +---w order                  int32
      |  |              |           |        +---w (action)?
      |  |              |           |           +--:(output-action-case)
      |  |              |           |           |  +---w output-action
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
      |  |              |           |           +--:(controller-action-case)
      |  |              |           |           |  +---w controller-action
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
      |  |              |           |           +--:(set-field-case)
      |  |              |           |           |  +---w set-field
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w metadata
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w tunnel
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w ethernet-match
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w vlan-match
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w ip-match
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8

      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
      |  |              |           |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
      |  |              |           |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)

      |  |              |           |           |     +---w queue?      string
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32

      |  |              |           |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp

      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix

      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!

      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)

      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w pbb
      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
      |  |              |           |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
      |  |              |           |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
      |  |              |           |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
      |  |              |           |           |  +---w set-queue-action
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w queue?      string
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32

      |  |              |           |     +---w table_id?   uint8
      |  |              |           +--:(write-metadata-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w write-metadata

      |  |              |           |     +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |           +--:(write-actions-case)

      |  |              |           |        +---w order                  int32
      |  |              |           |        +---w (action)?
      |  |              |           |           +--:(output-action-case)

      |  |              |           |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri

      |  |              |           |           +--:(controller-action-case)

      |  |              |           |           +--:(set-field-case)

      |  |              |           |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id

      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |           |           |     +---w ethernet-match
      |  |              |           |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address

      |  |              |           |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16

      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |  |              |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w pbb
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  |              |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
      |  |              |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
      |  |              |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-queue-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w queue?      string
      |  |              |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
      |  |              |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)

      |  |              |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
      |  |              |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-mpls-ttl-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w mpls-ttl?   uint8
      |  |              |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-nw-ttl-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w nw-ttl?   uint8
      |  |              |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

      |  |              |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

      |  |              |           |     +---w tag?             int32
      |  |              |           |     +---w pcp?             int32
      |  |              |           |     +---w cfi?             vlan-cfi

      |  |              |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)

      |  |              |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16

      |  |              |           +--:(set-field-case)

      |  |              |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  |              |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |  |              |           |     +---w metadata

      |  |              |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64

      |  |              |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |           |     +---w ethernet-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!

      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!

      |  |              |           |     +---w vlan-match

      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |              |           |     +---w ip-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8

      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |              |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix

      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label

      |  |              |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address

      |  |              |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
      |  |              |           +--:(controller-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w controller-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
      |  |              |           +--:(set-field-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-field
      |  |              |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  |              |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |  |              |           |     +---w metadata
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |           |     +---w tunnel
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |           |     +---w ethernet-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
      |  |              |           |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
      |  |              |           |     +---w vlan-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |              |           |     +---w ip-match
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |              |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |              |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?

      |  |              |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)

      |  |              |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix

      |  |              |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number

      |  |              |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-nw-dst-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w (address)?
      |  |              |           |        +--:(ipv4)
      |  |              |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |        +--:(ipv6)
      |  |              |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
