      |  |              |           |     +---w (address)?
      |  |              |           |        +--:(ipv4)
      |  |              |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |           |        +--:(ipv6)
      |  |              |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w tos?   int32
      |  |              |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
      |  |              |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-tp-src-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
      |  |              |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
      |  |              |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-vlan-id-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
      |  |              |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w set-vlan-pcp-action
      |  |              |           |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |              |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
      |  |              |           |  +---w strip-vlan-action
      |  |              |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
      |  |              |              +---w sw-path-action
      |  |              +--:(match)
      |  |              |  +---w match-setfield
      |  |              |     +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |              |        +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |              |        +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  |              +--:(wildcards)
      |  |              |  +---w wildcard-setfield
      |  |              |     +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |              |        +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |              |        +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  |              +--:(write-setfield)
      |  |              |  +---w write-setfield
      |  |              |     +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |              |        +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |              |        +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  |              +--:(write-setfield-miss)
      |  |              |  +---w write-setfield-miss
      |  |              |     +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |              |        +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |              |        +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  |              +--:(apply-setfield)
      |  |              |  +---w apply-setfield
      |  |              |     +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |              |        +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |              |        +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  |              +--:(apply-setfield-miss)
      |  |                 +---w apply-setfield-miss
      |  |                    +---w set-field-match* [match-type]
      |  |                       +---w match-type    identityref
      |  |                       +---w has-mask?     boolean
      |  +---w transaction-id?   transaction-id
      +--ro output    
         +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id

                  |           |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)

                  |           |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
                  |           |           |     +--ro icmpv6-match
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
                  |           |           |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro pbb
                  |           |           |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
                  |           |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
                  |           |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
                  |           |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
                  |           |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro set-queue-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro queue?      string
                  |           |           |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
                  |           |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)

                  |           |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)

                  |           |           |  +--ro push-pbb-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro pop-pbb-action
                  |           |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro push-mpls-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)

                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version

                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
                  |           |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
                  |           |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
                  |           |           |     +--ro icmpv4-match
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
                  |           |           |     +--ro icmpv6-match
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
                  |           |           |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro pbb
                  |           |           |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
                  |           |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
                  |           |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
                  |           |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
                  |           |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro set-queue-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro queue?      string
                  |           |           |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
                  |           |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
                  |           |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro set-nw-ttl-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro nw-ttl?   uint8
                  |           |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro push-pbb-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro pop-pbb-action
                  |           |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro push-mpls-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro dec-mpls-ttl
                  |           |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro dec-nw-ttl

                  |           |           +--:(flood-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro flood-action
                  |           |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro flood-all-action

                  |           |           |  +--ro loopback-action
                  |           |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro pop-vlan-action
                  |           |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro push-vlan-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           |           |     +--ro tag?             int32
                  |           |           |     +--ro pcp?             int32
                  |           |           |     +--ro cfi?             vlan-cfi
                  |           |           |     +--ro vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
                  |           |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-out
                  |           |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-in
                  |           |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)

                  |           |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
                  |           |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro set-dl-src-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address

                  |           |           |  +--ro group-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro group?      string
                  |           |           |     +--ro group-id?   uint32
                  |           |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro set-dl-type-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
                  |           |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro set-next-hop-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro (address)?
                  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |           |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)

                  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |           |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix

                  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)

                  |           |              +--ro sw-path-action

                  |              +--ro meter
                  |                 +--ro meter-id?   meter:meter-id
                  +--:(next-table)
                  |  +--ro tables
                  |     +--ro table-ids*   uint8
                  +--:(next-table-miss)
                  |  +--ro tables-miss
                  |     +--ro table-ids*   uint8

                  |  +--ro write-actions
                  |     +--ro action* [order]
                  |        +--ro order                  int32
                  |        +--ro (action)?
                  |           +--:(output-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro output-action

                  |           +--:(controller-action-case)

                  |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
                  |           |     +--ro metadata
                  |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
                  |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
                  |           |     +--ro tunnel
                  |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
                  |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!

                  |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
                  |           |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!

                  |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
                  |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  |           |     +--ro ip-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8

                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8

                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)

                  |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix

                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8

                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8

                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
                  |           |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
                  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
                  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro pbb
                  |           |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
                  |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
                  |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
                  |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
                  |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-queue-action
                  |           |     +--ro queue?      string
                  |           |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
                  |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action

                  |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-nw-ttl-action
                  |           |     +--ro nw-ttl?   uint8
                  |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro push-pbb-action

                  |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro pop-pbb-action
                  |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)

                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
                  |           |  +--ro dec-mpls-ttl
                  |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
                  |           |  +--ro dec-nw-ttl
                  |           +--:(drop-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro drop-action
                  |           +--:(flood-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro flood-action
                  |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)

                  |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-next-hop-action
                  |           |     +--ro (address)?
                  |           |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |        +--:(ipv6)

                  |  +--ro apply-actions

                  |        +--ro order                  int32
                  |        +--ro (action)?

                  |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

                  |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64

                  |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
                  |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
                  |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
                  |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix

                  |           |  +--ro drop-action
                  |           +--:(flood-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro flood-action
                  |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro flood-all-action
                  |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro hw-path-action
                  |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro loopback-action
                  |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro pop-vlan-action
                  |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro push-vlan-action
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           |     +--ro tag?             int32
                  |           |     +--ro pcp?             int32
                  |           |     +--ro cfi?             vlan-cfi
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
                  |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
                  |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-out
                  |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
                  |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-in
                  |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-dl-dst-action
                  |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
                  |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-dl-src-action
                  |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
                  |           +--:(group-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro group-action
                  |           |     +--ro group?      string
                  |           |     +--ro group-id?   uint32
                  |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-dl-type-action
                  |           |     +--ro dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
                  |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-next-hop-action
                  |           |     +--ro (address)?
                  |           |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-nw-dst-action
                  |           |     +--ro (address)?
                  |           |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-nw-src-action
                  |           |     +--ro (address)?
                  |           |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
                  |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
                  |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
                  |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
                  |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
                  |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
                  |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
                  |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
                  |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
                  |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
                  |              +--ro sw-path-action
                  +--:(match)
                  |  +--ro match-setfield
                  |     +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                  |        +--ro match-type    identityref
                  |        +--ro has-mask?     boolean
                  +--:(wildcards)
                  |  +--ro wildcard-setfield
                  |     +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                  |        +--ro match-type    identityref
                  |        +--ro has-mask?     boolean
                  +--:(write-setfield)
                  |  +--ro write-setfield
                  |     +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                  |        +--ro match-type    identityref
                  |        +--ro has-mask?     boolean
                  +--:(write-setfield-miss)
                  |  +--ro write-setfield-miss
                  |     +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                  |        +--ro match-type    identityref
                  |        +--ro has-mask?     boolean
                  +--:(apply-setfield)
                  |  +--ro apply-setfield
                  |     +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                  |        +--ro match-type    identityref
                  |        +--ro has-mask?     boolean
                  +--:(apply-setfield-miss)
                     +--ro apply-setfield-miss
                        +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                           +--ro match-type    identityref
                           +--ro has-mask?     boolean
module: shutdown-impl
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(shutdown)
      +--rw secret?   string
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:state:
   +--:(shutdown)
rpcs:
   +---x shutdown    
      +---w input     
         +---w context-instance?   instance-identifier
         +---w input-secret?       string
         +---w max-wait-time?      uint32
         +---w reason?             string
module: statistics-manager
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(statistics-manager)
      +--rw rpc-registry
      |  +--rw type    service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw notification-service
      |  +--rw type    service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw data-broker
      |  +--rw type?   service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw statistics-manager-settings
         +--rw min-request-net-monitor-interval?   int32
         +--rw max-nodes-for-collector?            int32
module: stp-status-aware-node-connector
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/inv:node-connector:
   +--rw status?   stp-status
module: system-notifications
notifications:
   +---n disconnect-event     
   |  +--ro info?   string
   +---n switch-idle-event    
      +--ro info?   string
module: threadgroup
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(netty-threadgroup-fixed)
      +--rw thread-count?   uint16
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:state:
   +--:(netty-threadgroup-fixed)
module: threadpool-impl-fixed
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(threadpool-fixed)
      +--rw max-thread-count?   uint16
      +--rw threadFactory
         +--rw type    service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
module: threadpool-impl-flexible
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(threadpool-flexible)
      +--rw max-thread-count?   uint16
      +--rw minThreadCount?     uint16
      +--rw keepAliveMillis?    uint32
      +--rw queueCapacity?      uint16
      +--rw threadFactory
         +--rw type    service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
module: threadpool-impl-scheduled
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(threadpool-scheduled)
      +--rw max-thread-count?   uint16
      +--rw threadFactory
         +--rw type    service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
module: threadpool-impl
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(eventbus)
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:state:
   +--:(eventbus)
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(async-eventbus)
      +--rw threadpool
         +--rw type    service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:state:
   +--:(async-eventbus)
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(threadfactory-naming)
      +--rw name-prefix?   string
rpcs:
   +---x get-dead-events-count    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w context-instance?   instance-identifier
      +--ro output    
         +--ro result?   uint32
